Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:04.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}世界环保日  波士顿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:15.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的表停了\N{\rEng}It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:16.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了  大卫\N{\rEng}What's that, Dave?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:17.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,没什么\N{\rEng}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:18.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,准备得怎么样\N{\rEng}How we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.27,0:01:19.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,哦  准备好了\N{\rEng}Oh, we're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:21.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有信心吗\N{\rEng}You feeling the magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.74,0:01:22.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,有  我信心十足  很好\N{\rEng}Oh, I'm feeling the magic, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.83,0:01:23.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们去说服他们\N{\rEng}Let's hit them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.87,0:01:24.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.94,0:01:26.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\rEng}Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.29,0:01:27.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,走\N{\rEng}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.13,0:01:27.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们去说服他们\N{\rEng}Let's hit them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.91,0:01:31.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们要拿到这３千万\N{\rEng}Let's go make $30 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.13,0:01:37.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,大家好\N{\rEng}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:41.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,开始之前  让我…\N{\rEng}Before I begin, let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:49.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,大卫\N{\rEng}David?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:51.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我去叫人来\N{\rEng}I'll go get help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:54.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,天呐  大卫\N{\rEng}Jesus. Jesus, David.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:56.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,快打911  快打911\N{\rEng}Phone 9-1-1. Phone 9-1-1!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.54,0:01:57.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,大卫\N{\rEng}David?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:06.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\N{\rEng}Nick?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.97,0:02:09.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  尼克\N{\rEng}Nicky?Nicky!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:35.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了  没事了\N{\rEng}Okay, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:36.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,没事了\N{\rEng}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.98,0:02:39.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都从车上下来\N{\rEng}Everybody else off the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:48.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,声波\N{\rEng}Sound waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:53.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们知道当声波\N{\rEng}So, if we know that sound waves
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:58.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,穿越越来越多的障碍物后\N{\rEng}gain wavelength and lose frequency
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:02.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,它的波长增加而频率减少\N{\rEng}as they travel through more dense materials...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:07.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们就可以据此确定声场中\N{\rEng}...then the anomalies in these waves
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:10.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,不规则物体的形状和位置\N{\rEng}are the means by which we can surmise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:13.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,据此我们也可以分析地球的构造\N{\rEng}the fundamental architecture of our planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:17.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,克丽丝汀  你的指甲怎么了\N{\rEng}How are the nails coming, Christine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:21.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rEng}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:23.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,下面  让我们来做个示范\N{\rEng}All right, let's have a demonstration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:26.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾克先生 维罗妮卡  麻烦你们\N{\rEng}Mr. Acker, Veronica.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:28.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,十分感谢\N{\rEng}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:31.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:34.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们知道  莱仕东夫人很大但也很柔软\N{\rEng}Mrs. Limestone, being a big softie, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:36.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢在公园散步  听枕边故事\N{\rEng}Ioves walks in the park, bedtime stories,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:37.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,很浪漫的那种\N{\rEng}big romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:38.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢甜言蜜语\N{\rEng}Loves Chet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不懂甜言蜜语 但我来看看能做些什么\N{\rEng}I can't play Chet, but I'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:42.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,盯着示波器  好了吗\N{\rEng}Watch the oscilloscope, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,仔细看着\N{\rEng}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:54.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,约书亚·凯斯博士\N{\rEng}Dr. Joshua Keyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:03:55.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,也许\N{\rEng}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:57.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,是还是不是\N{\rEng}Yes or no, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:03:59.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\rEng}The first one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,先生  请跟我们来\N{\rEng}Please come with us, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:06.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们出了什么事\N{\rEng}Guys, wh-what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:07.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们也不知道  先生\N{\rEng}We don't know, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:10.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么  你们也不知道\N{\rEng}What do you mean, you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:13.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,您的忠诚调查评价比我们要高\N{\rEng}Your security clearance is higher than ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:15.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,我做过忠诚调查\N{\rEng}I have security clearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:17.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们一到您的飞机那儿去\N{\rEng}We're just here to bring you to your jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:19.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,我有飞机\N{\rEng}I have a jet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:22.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}华盛顿特区
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:38.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,你好  赛吉\N{\rEng}Hey, Serge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:41.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,-赛吉  赛吉  -妈的\N{\rEng}-Serge Serge -Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:44.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,到时间了．你总是迟到\N{\rEng}It's about time. You're always late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:47.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,走吧  先生们\N{\rEng}Let's keep moving, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:48.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,要我来这里干什么啊\N{\rEng}What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:51.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,在你来到之前  他们都不给我说\N{\rEng}They wouldn't brief me until you got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里到处都是军方的生物化学工作者\N{\rEng}You know, there are biochemists everywhere, military.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:55.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌他们\N{\rEng}I hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:57.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候能找到个好女孩\N{\rEng}When are you going to meet a nice girl
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:04:58.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,和她一起共进晚餐呢\N{\rEng}and bring her for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:04:59.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,我几经和我的工作结婚了\N{\rEng}I'm married to my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:04:59.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\rEng}So am l.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:02.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,她既是妻子又是情人\N{\rEng}Which makes my wife my mistress...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:04.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以我深爱着她\N{\rEng}that's why I'm still in love with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,你总是这么浪漫啊\N{\rEng}You were always a romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:08.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我爱我的妻子\N{\rEng}I love my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的．我也很爱你的妻子\N{\rEng}Yeah, I know. I love your wife, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:11.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\rEng}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:13.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我并不爱你的那个妻子 你知道我在说什么\N{\rEng}But I don't love your wife. You know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,你爱她的方式和我不一样  你知道的\N{\rEng}You don't love her the same way, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:18.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是个法国式的笑话\N{\rEng}It's the French. I think it's the cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:19.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,法式的\N{\rEng}The cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:21.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在…你在考我吗\N{\rEng}You're... you're teasing me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:22.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,噢  天\N{\rEng}Oh, my...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:24.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些是尸体\N{\rEng}Wait, these are bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:26.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们是不是来错地方了\N{\rEng}I think we're in the wrong place here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:27.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该是走错地方了\N{\rEng}Yeah, we're in the wrong place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:29.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  如果你们真的走错了地方\N{\rEng}No. If you were in the wrong place,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:31.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,早就打死了\N{\rEng}you would've already been shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:33.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是个疯狂的问候啊\N{\rEng}That's a hell of a greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:35.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,赛吉\N{\rEng}Serge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:36.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,赛吉\N{\rEng}Serge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:38.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  赛吉  很荣幸见到你\N{\rEng}Serge. Yes. Always a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:39.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,很荣幸  托马斯\N{\rEng}Same here, Thomas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:40.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,凯斯  博士\N{\rEng}Dr. Keyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:42.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我知道  -汤姆·珀塞尔\N{\rEng}-I know. -Tom Purcell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,先生们  我想你们已经知道\N{\rEng}Gentlemen, you do realize that everything here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:48.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里的一切都是顶极机密的\N{\rEng}is totally classified, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:52.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,在当地时间早上10点30分\N{\rEng}At 10:30 a.m. Iocal time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:56.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,在10个街区的范围内  32个市民\N{\rEng}32 civilians, all within a 10-block radius...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:58.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,都死了\N{\rEng}died.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们在之前并没有生病\N{\rEng}They didn't get sick first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:02.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们很简单得倒在地上死了\N{\rEng}They simply hit the ground dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:03.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有别的原因\N{\rEng}Nerve agent?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的初步猜测是…  没有\N{\rEng}Our first guess. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们是在同一时间死掉的\N{\rEng}They all died at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:08.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,据我们的调查结果  就是在同一时间\N{\rEng}As far as we can tell, to the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:10.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,这件事一小时之内就震动了美国有线新闻网络\N{\rEng}This hits CNN in one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:11.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,我需要答案\N{\rEng}I need a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:13.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,在性别  年龄或者身体特征方面产生了什么变异吗\N{\rEng}Is there a variation in sex, age, body type?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:15.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们都安装了内置的心脏起搏器\N{\rEng}They all had pacemakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:17.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,一分钟之内就反应过来\N{\rEng}Under a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:19.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是名不虚传\N{\rEng}Your reputation is well deserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:23.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,在没有检查过受害者之前\N{\rEng}How did you guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:24.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么猜到的\N{\rEng}Without any clues from the victims?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:26.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,不…\N{\rEng}No, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:27.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,赛吉和我就是线索吧\N{\rEng}Serge and I are the clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:29.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  他精通的是高能量武器\N{\rEng}I mean, he specializes in high energy weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:30.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,而我是地磁方面的专家\N{\rEng}I do geomagnetics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:32.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,叫我们来  就是说你们怀疑\N{\rEng}So calling us means you suspect
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:34.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是一种电磁脉冲武器\N{\rEng}an electromagnetic pulse weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:36.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果这只是天灾\N{\rEng}If these are the only fatalities,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:38.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们一定是很容易\N{\rEng}they must be people susceptible to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,受电磁波影响的人\N{\rEng}electronic interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,QED型心脏起搏器\N{\rEng}QED pacemakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:43.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,有时候你真像鬼一样精明\N{\rEng}You're spooky sometimes, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:44.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道的是\N{\rEng}Now I need to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:46.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些人被一种武器所杀的可能性有多大\N{\rEng}did some sort of weapon kill these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:47.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,要造成足够强度的EM脉冲\N{\rEng}The power that you would need
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:49.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,所需要的能量…\N{\rEng}to create an EM pulse strong enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  我从没听说过这样一种武器\N{\rEng}I mean, that's... that's not a weapon thatI've ever heard of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:52.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:54.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  我们的工作完成了\N{\rEng}Okay, we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:56.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,还没有完啊  先生\N{\rEng}We're not done, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:59.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,等号的另一边还是空的\N{\rEng}There's nothing on the other side of the equal sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我同意约书亚说的\N{\rEng}I agree with Joshua...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:01.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:03.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们最关心的是这次事件是不是一场军事袭击\N{\rEng}Our greatest concern was this may have been an act of war,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在确认它不是\N{\rEng}but since it's not,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:06.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们可以放轻松一些了  不是吗\N{\rEng}I think we can all breathe a little easier, can't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:15.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}伦敦  特拉法尔加广场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:27.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,看我的帽子\N{\rEng}Look at my hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:36.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了  亲爱的\N{\rEng}What is it, sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,这没什么  儿子\N{\rEng}It's okay, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:46.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,这种事情每时每刻都在发生 并且…\N{\rEng}These things happen all the time and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:57.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\rEng}Let's, go, let's go! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:15.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,贾斯廷\N{\rEng}Justin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:20.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,看着点  你这白痴\N{\rEng}Watch out, you bloody idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:27.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,快啊  快跑\N{\rEng}Hurry! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:11.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\rEng}Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:25.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在  纳尔逊广场的上空一无所有\N{\rEng}The skies are empty over Nelson's Column now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:27.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,但就在几个小时之前  又是不同的情景\N{\rEng}but a few hours ago, it was a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:29.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,目击者声称狂乱的鸟群\N{\rEng}Eyewitnesses claimed that the frenzied swarms of birds
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:32.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,并不是在有意攻击人类\N{\rEng}were not in fact attacking people deliberately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:34.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,并不是只有这一次  不不不不不\N{\rEng}And it's not just this time. No, no, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:35.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,而是看上去毫无目的盲目的乱飞\N{\rEng}but seemed to be confused and flying blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:37.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,这本杂志上报道过类似的事件\N{\rEng}The Fortean Times reported violent bird swarms
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:39.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,上个月在澳大利亚和日本出现过2次狂乱的鸟群\N{\rEng}twice last month in Australia and Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:41.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,（据证实已有5人死亡上百人受伤）\N{\rEng}(Five people are confirmed dead and dozens injured)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:43.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,（在惊恐之后是巨大的疑问  不久之后同样的事件发生在）\N{\rEng}(in the panic that followed the bizarre and terrifying incident)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:45.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,（伦敦著名的特拉法尔加广场）\N{\rEng}(in London's historic T rafalgar Square.)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:46.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是怪异\N{\rEng}Weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:47.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,这也太奇怪了\N{\rEng}Quite strange, also.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:49.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,确实很奇怪\N{\rEng}Strange, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:55.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,鸟类是怎样辨认方向的\N{\rEng}How do birds navigate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:56.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,靠视力\N{\rEng}By sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,不不不  我是说在长距离迁徙时\N{\rEng}No, no, no, the long range stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.69,0:09:59.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,地磁力场\N{\rEng}Magnetic fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们的脑子里有一种\N{\rEng}Little ions in their brains
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:03.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,与地磁力场相关的微小粒子\N{\rEng}align with the magnetic field of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:06.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,-对  就是她说的  -对吗\N{\rEng}-Yeah, what she said. -Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:07.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,涡流\N{\rEng}Acker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:09.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们到网上  找找…\N{\rEng}Hit the 'Net, do a search for...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:11.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,噢  2年内的\N{\rEng}oh, two years ought to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:13.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,所有的超自然事件的新闻  主要是关于\N{\rEng}Any and all, like, "weird news", you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:14.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,奇异的动物迁徙\N{\rEng}bizarre animal migrations,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:16.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是鸟类\N{\rEng}specifically birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:17.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,鲸鱼和海豚的海滩搁浅\N{\rEng}Whale and dolphin beachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:20.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,不正常的大气现象  原因不明的飞机坠毁\N{\rEng}Unusual atmospheric phenomenon, unexplained plane crashes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:22.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,发挥你的想象力\N{\rEng}you know, just use your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:23.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个查找可是工作量巨大啊\N{\rEng}That is a huge search.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能用我们的T1专线来看《水手月》  废物\N{\rEng}You can use our T-1 line to look up Sailor Moon crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:27.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,你也只能干这个了\N{\rEng}You're up to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:28.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,唐丹妮 唐丹妮  \N{\rEng}Danni, Danni
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:28.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,帮我在“场论”专业的班级里\N{\rEng}get me the brightest kids
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,找几个最聪明小子来\N{\rEng}from the Field Theory Class,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:32.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,帮我设计个电磁场的模型\N{\rEng}and design a computer model of an electromagnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:33.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们该干些什么\N{\rEng}What are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:35.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我需要一个地球的立体模型\N{\rEng}I need a 3-D computer model of the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:36.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,来放置这个磁场模型\N{\rEng}to lay the field over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:37.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,地球的\N{\rEng}the planet Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:40.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  地球的  就是那个漂亮的蓝色星球\N{\rEng}Yeah, the planet Earth. You know, the pretty blue one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:42.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,在地图上标出找到的不规则的涡流\N{\rEng}Map out the anomalies that Acker finds
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:43.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,并构造出方程式\N{\rEng}and grunt out the equations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:44.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,并且\N{\rEng}And
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:46.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,去找一些研究非线性理论的\N{\rEng}grab those smelly kids
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:47.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,班级里那些臭烘烘小子来\N{\rEng}from the Non-Linear Diff class, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.97,0:10:49.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,听我说约书亚  我们还有时间干这些吗\N{\rEng}Listen, Josh, do we even have time for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:52.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,老老实实给我干活  你的博士学位就没问题了\N{\rEng}Do this and I'll sign your doctorates blindfolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:53.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,-快到手了  -是的\N{\rEng}-Blindfolded? -Blindfolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:55.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,不用考试  直接拿到博士学位\N{\rEng}Do not pass Go. Go directly to PhD.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.19,0:11:04.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,但愿是我错了  但愿是我错了\N{\rEng}Be wrong. Be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:02.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,蒂姆  我有些紧张\N{\rEng}Tim, I'm coming in a little hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:03.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,能帮我一下吗\N{\rEng}Give me some drag, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:04.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,行啊\N{\rEng}Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:17.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经调整好进入入射界面角度\N{\rEng}We are in attitude and ready for an entry interface.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:18.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,做的好  少校\N{\rEng}Nice work, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:21.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,我接手控制了\N{\rEng}I have the controls now for E.I.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:23.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,交给我好了\N{\rEng}I could take us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:25.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能够…\N{\rEng}You could...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:26.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,但你不可以\N{\rEng}but you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:27.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,我已经做好准备了\N{\rEng}I'm ready for this, Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:28.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  小贝你没有\N{\rEng}No, you're not, Beck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:31.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,虽然你受过这方面的训练而且也是合格的\N{\rEng}You're trained, and you're certified
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:32.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,但别把自己当作指挥官\N{\rEng}doesn't make you the commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:34.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,你现在还没有资格指挥着陆行动\N{\rEng}And the commander lands the bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:37.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,你应该是进入太空的人当中最年轻的了\N{\rEng}You got to be the youngest person ever in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:38.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,你应该说“谢谢” 开心点吧\N{\rEng}You should say, thank you, be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:39.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\rEng}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:43.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾德华号  这里是休斯敦基地\N{\rEng}Endeavour, Houston, at this time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:45.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在给你们导航\N{\rEng}We show you go for reentry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:47.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,休斯敦基地  艾德华号的距离缩短到400 000英尺\N{\rEng}Houston, Endeavour descending through 400, 000 feet
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:49.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,就要到达进入面\N{\rEng}coming upon entry interface.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:50.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾德华号  这是弗莱特\N{\rEng}Endeavour, this is Flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:52.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,这次又没有说服指挥官\N{\rEng}Weren't able to annoy the commander
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:54.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,让你驾驶着陆吧\N{\rEng}into letting you bring her in this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:54.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,确实是没有  史迪克\N{\rEng}That's a negative, Stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:56.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,下次我一定要多给他找点麻烦\N{\rEng}I'll have to be more annoying next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:57.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,你认为这有用吗\N{\rEng}Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:12:59.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾德华号\N{\rEng}Endeavour,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:01.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们看见你进来了  调整得很好\N{\rEng}we see you in good entry config.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,收到  休斯敦\N{\rEng}Roger, Houston.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:07.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,警告\N{\rEng}Advise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:10.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,我看见一片等离子区域\N{\rEng}I'm seeing those plasma trails now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:11.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  标记为24  1/2\N{\rEng}All right, mark 24 1/2.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:12.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有一分钟接触大气层\N{\rEng}So, a minute to air.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:14.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信安全带\N{\rEng}I don't believe in belts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:21.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,只要这艘船能带我穿越大气层\N{\rEng}Just get me through the Earth's atmosphere in this spaceship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:24.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,信号丢失\N{\rEng}Com dropout.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,开始接收\N{\rEng}Start the I Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:39.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们等到…\N{\rEng}Let's wait till the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:41.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,信号恢复\N{\rEng}Com restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:45.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}警告  偏离轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:51.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,安静\N{\rEng}Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:58.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们偏离航向了\N{\rEng}We are out of position here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:00.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,领航系统显示我们在正确的位置上\N{\rEng}Guidance shows us on energy and on course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:03.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在模拟训练中走过213次这条路线\N{\rEng}Well, I've made this approach 213 times in the simulator.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:04.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不应该在这\N{\rEng}We're not where we should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:05.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们到底在哪里\N{\rEng}Where the hell are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:09.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾德华号  领航系统故障了\N{\rEng}Endeavour, guidance is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:12.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们偏离航道102英里\N{\rEng}You are now 1-2-niner miles off course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:14.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,收到  休斯敦基地 我们多少也注意到了\N{\rEng}Roger, Houston. We sort of noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:15.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,那里是…\N{\rEng}Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,洛杉矶  这点可以确定\N{\rEng}Los Angeles. That is confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:18.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的高度只有105 000英尺了\N{\rEng}We are 1-5 thousand feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:21.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们只剩下2分钟\N{\rEng}We got maybe two minutes of glide time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:22.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,说这些都是无意义的\N{\rEng}Doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:24.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,领航和灯塔系统都坏了吗\N{\rEng}The guidance, the beacons are all wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:27.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们正笔直地飞向市区\N{\rEng}We're heading straight for downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:28.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能撞击洛杉矶啊\N{\rEng}We're not going to crash into Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:29.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们会以300节的速度\N{\rEng}They're going to hit downtown L.A.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:30.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,撞击洛杉矶\N{\rEng}at 300 knots.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:35.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,鲍勃  你知道洛杉矶吗  我有个主意\N{\rEng}Bob, you know L.A.? Because I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:37.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,休斯敦基地  那些建筑物越来越大了\N{\rEng}Houston, those buildings are getting mighty big.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们能清理出一条高速公路吗\N{\rEng}Can you clear a freeway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:41.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  谢谢\N{\rEng}Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:42.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,快呀  快呀\N{\rEng}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:45.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在是繁忙时间  指挥官\N{\rEng}It's rush hour, Commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:46.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,路上的车一辆接一辆的\N{\rEng}and it's bumper-to-bumper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:50.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,长官  我有个替代方案\N{\rEng}Sir, I have an alternate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:52.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你朝向10705…\N{\rEng}If you turn to heading 1-7-5...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:53.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,呼叫休斯敦基地  休斯敦\N{\rEng}It's Houston's call. Houston?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:56.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,计算机还在测绘\N{\rEng}Computers are still plotting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:58.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,快呀\N{\rEng}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:19.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,休斯敦\N{\rEng}Houston, we are running
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:19.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们没多少时间了\N{\rEng}out of time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,长官  我有个替代方案\N{\rEng}Sir, I have an alternate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:22.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  小贝  你想说什么\N{\rEng}All right, Beck, what do you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:23.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,休斯敦  我找到个\N{\rEng}Houston, I have coordinates
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:24.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,替代的降落地点\N{\rEng}for an alternate landing site.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:25.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能批准吗\N{\rEng}Can you confirm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:27.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾德华号  把资料给我\N{\rEng}Endeavour, give them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:31.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,我找到的地点是北纬33.55  西经118.10\N{\rEng}I show possible touchdown... at 33.55 north, 118.10 west.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:34.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,比尔\N{\rEng}Bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:36.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,理论上是可以的\N{\rEng}It's theoretically possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:37.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾德华号\N{\rEng}Endeavour,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:38.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,提案批准\N{\rEng}that is confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:41.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,右转  航向10705\N{\rEng}T urn right, heading 1-7-5.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.70,0:15:42.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,5秒之内和洛杉矶河\N{\rEng}Expect visual contact
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:45.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,来一次亲密接触吧\N{\rEng}with Los Angeles River in five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:51.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  休斯敦基地  这行不通\N{\rEng}No, that will not work, Houston.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:53.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,每隔几百米就有一座桥\N{\rEng}We got bridges every few hundred yards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:55.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们会死的\N{\rEng}Our wingspan alone is going to fold us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:56.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,我已经演算过了\N{\rEng}I've figured the "L" over "D" max.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.75,0:15:58.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,可以做得到  只要你带我们直直的飞过去\N{\rEng}We can make it if you can bring us straight in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:15:59.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,太疯狂了\N{\rEng}We're coming in high and hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:07.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,290英尺  320节\N{\rEng}290 feet, 320.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:08.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,放下轮子\N{\rEng}-270, 3-0-5... -Arm the gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:10.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,启动完成\N{\rEng}You're armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:10.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,放下起落架\N{\rEng}Gear down. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:12.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,放下了\N{\rEng}Gear in transition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:20.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,240英尺  290节\N{\rEng}240 feet, 290.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:22.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住  现在需要精确的控制\N{\rEng}Hang on. This isn't going to be subtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:27.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,210英尺  265节\N{\rEng}210 feet, 265.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:30.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,离开路面  快跑\N{\rEng}Get out of the way! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:34.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,反旋 \N{\rEng}Derotate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:35.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,向内\N{\rEng}Inward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:42.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,230…210…\N{\rEng}230...210...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:44.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,紧急刹车\N{\rEng}Speed brakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,100%启动\N{\rEng}100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:46.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们太快了\N{\rEng}We're way too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:47.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,展开侧斜翼\N{\rEng}Deploy the chute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:50.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  会撞上桥的 我们从下面穿过去\N{\rEng}No. We'd snag the bridge. We'll tear the tail off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.27,0:16:55.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,向右转\N{\rEng}Banking right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,指挥官  下一座桥\N{\rEng}Commander, that next bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:02.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,注意\N{\rEng}Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:04.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们太高了\N{\rEng}We're way too high for that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:05.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,收起轮子\N{\rEng}Suck up the gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:06.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在还不行  我们会失去控制的\N{\rEng}Not yet. We'll lose all steering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:08.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果撞上了  就都完了\N{\rEng}We hit, it's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:14.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在…收起轮子\N{\rEng}And... gear up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:22.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,抓紧了  现在我没法控制它了\N{\rEng}Lock your harnesses. This is out of my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:39.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,快离开这里\N{\rEng}Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:42.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,跑啊  快跑\N{\rEng}Run! Let's get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:17.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}自然科学学院
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:22.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}康拉德辛斯基博士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:27.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,辛斯基博士\N{\rEng}Dr. Zimsky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:29.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能把电话号码留给我的助手吗  亲爱的\N{\rEng}Will you make sure my assistant has your number, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:29.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:31.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,辛斯基博士\N{\rEng}Dr. Zimsky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:33.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  这很好  这很好．你好\N{\rEng}No, it's all right. It's all right. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:36.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,-辛斯基博士  -是的  你叫什么\N{\rEng}-Dr. Zimsky. -Yes. What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:38.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,-约书亚·凯斯  -约书亚\N{\rEng}-Josh Keyes. -Josh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:40.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,不先生  我不是来要你得签名的\N{\rEng}No, sir, I don't need you to sign it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:41.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要你读一下这个\N{\rEng}I need you to read that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:42.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  我没有时间\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, I don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:45.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,白宫的会议我已经迟到了\N{\rEng}I'm late for the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:46.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你来确定我的研究发现\N{\rEng}I need you to confirm my results, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,年轻人  你知道我是谁吗\N{\rEng}Young man, do you have any idea who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:51.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的先生  请你读一下这个\N{\rEng}Yes, I do, sir. Please read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:55.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\rEng}What's it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:19:00.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,世界的末日\N{\rEng}It's the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:26.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  我想…  这不可能  对不起\N{\rEng}No, l... this is impossible. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:28.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,我  我  我不会错过这些现象的\N{\rEng}I-l-I can't have missed this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:30.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,你一定是错了\N{\rEng}You-You have to be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  我很肯定\N{\rEng}I mean, look, I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:33.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,仔细地和我的研究结论对比一下\N{\rEng}with careful comparison to my own work,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:34.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,很明显你搞错了\N{\rEng}we'll find that you are mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:36.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,不需要争辨  但是…\N{\rEng}No offense, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:38.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  我们很快就会了解的\N{\rEng}Well, I mean, we'll know soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.42,0:19:42.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在  还有好多怪异的现象会发生\N{\rEng}The bigger effects will start up any day now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:07.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}机密文件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:43.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,蕾贝卡\N{\rEng}Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:46.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,只有你和父亲还在这么叫我\N{\rEng}Only you and Dad ever call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:48.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  小贝\N{\rEng}Well, Beck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:50.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么到华盛顿来了\N{\rEng}So, what brings you to sunny D.C.?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:52.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,下周就是飞行评测了\N{\rEng}The Board of Review is next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:57.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想探听一下上面的意思\N{\rEng}Just trying to get a sense of the mood upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:20:58.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,有多糟糕\N{\rEng}How bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:00.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们撞毁了那架航天飞机\N{\rEng}Your crew crashed the space shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:02.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们的心情还能好到哪去\N{\rEng}Now, how good do you think it could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:06.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,先生  这是我的生命\N{\rEng}Sir, this is my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:07.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,是吗…\N{\rEng}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:09.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,我13岁开始  就在专门的学校学习\N{\rEng}I was studying for the academy when I was 1 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:11.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的生命啊\N{\rEng}It still is and has always been my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:13.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,结束了\N{\rEng}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:16.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,结束了  蕾贝卡\N{\rEng}It's over, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:18.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉\N{\rEng}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:20.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,就发生在下面\N{\rEng}It's right down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.37,0:21:21.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,真的\N{\rEng}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.37,0:21:22.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,那就好像7月14的焰火\N{\rEng}It's like the 4th of July.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:23.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,这怎么这么繁忙啊\N{\rEng}What the hell's the hurry here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:29.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,蕾贝卡  我能离开一下吗\N{\rEng}Rebecca, would you excuse me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:31.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\rEng}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:35.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,珀塞尔\N{\rEng}Purcell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:41.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,托马斯\N{\rEng}Thomas, um, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:43.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,命运真是捉弄人\N{\rEng}It seems that destiny may have caught up with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.36,0:22:06.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,辛斯基真的要给你他的亲笔签名\N{\rEng}Did Zimsky really try to give you his autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.25,0:22:11.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,啊  辛斯基先生\N{\rEng}Ah, Monsieur Zimsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:12.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,康拉德·辛斯基\N{\rEng}Conrad Zimsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:14.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,辛斯基先生\N{\rEng}Herr Zimsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.23,0:22:15.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,超级明星\N{\rEng}Superstar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.07,0:22:24.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我已经戒酒了\N{\rEng}I think I skipped drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:28.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,喝醉的滋味可不好受\N{\rEng}Went right to hangover.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.21,0:22:31.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不也是吗\N{\rEng}Weren't you the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:32.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,我和孩子们聊过了\N{\rEng}I spoke with the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.88,0:22:35.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们现在晚上都不睡觉了\N{\rEng}They don't sleep at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.28,0:22:40.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们看着天空  并且…他们认为这样很美\N{\rEng}They look at the sky, and... and they think it's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.49,0:22:43.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,不会是你弄错了吧\N{\rEng}Is there any chance you're wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:45.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  天空  伙计\N{\rEng}No. The sky, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.22,0:22:46.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  天空变成这样只是个开始\N{\rEng}The sky-- I mean, that's just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:48.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是高层空间的静电放电效果\N{\rEng}That's high-altitude static discharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.39,0:22:50.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rEng}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:52.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,凯斯博士…\N{\rEng}Dr. Keyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:57.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,…你必须出席在五角大楼召开的会议\N{\rEng}...your presence is required at the Pentagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.30,0:22:59.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,原来是我军方的老朋友啊\N{\rEng}It's my best buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.29,0:23:03.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不来和我们一起喝一杯呢\N{\rEng}Why don't you join us for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.24,0:23:05.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你随我们来的话我们将不胜感激  先生\N{\rEng}We'd be grateful if you could join us for a ride, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:07.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我说不呢\N{\rEng}And if I were to say no?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.39,0:23:09.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,就问问\N{\rEng}Just asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.25,0:23:11.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个…我们没有幽默感\N{\rEng}Well, we have no sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.48,0:23:12.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,这倒是真的\N{\rEng}That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.92,0:23:16.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我们有枪\N{\rEng}And we're armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.26,0:23:21.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:26.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎你  凯斯博士\N{\rEng}Dr. Keyes, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.13,0:23:27.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:28.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,辛斯基博士告诉我们\N{\rEng}Dr. Zimsky informs us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.77,0:23:30.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,你为他的研究做出了有用的贡献\N{\rEng}that you made a useful contribution
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.77,0:23:32.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以他希望你\N{\rEng}to his investigations, so he wanted you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.84,0:23:34.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,来做他报告的助手\N{\rEng}to assist him in the briefing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.34,0:23:36.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,你可真是慷慨啊  辛斯基博士\N{\rEng}That's very generous of you, Dr. Zimsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.11,0:23:38.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,小伙子  科学是无私的事业\N{\rEng}Science is a selfless business, dear boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:41.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在  为什么不开始呢\N{\rEng}Now, why don't you begin,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.55,0:23:44.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会在一些难点上加以解释的\N{\rEng}and I'll fill in all the difficult bits.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.62,0:23:50.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  我会尽量的说得简单一些\N{\rEng}All right, I'll put this as simply as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.56,0:23:53.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,一年之内地球上所有的人都会死掉\N{\rEng}Everybody on Earth is dead in a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.43,0:23:57.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,让我来解释为什么\N{\rEng}And let me explain why.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.30,0:24:01.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的地球是被一种无形的能量包裹着的\N{\rEng}Wrapped around the Earth is an invisible field of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.20,0:24:03.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,它由电荷与磁力构成\N{\rEng}It's made up of... electricity and magnetism,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:05.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以它被称为\N{\rEng}so it's called creatively enough
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.97,0:24:07.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,电磁场\N{\rEng}the electromagnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.47,0:24:10.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,这也就是北磁极和南磁极的成因\N{\rEng}It's where we get our magnetic North Pole and South Pole,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.74,0:24:13.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,并且它还保护我们不受宇宙射线的伤害\N{\rEng}and it protects us from cosmic radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.08,0:24:15.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以这个磁场是我们的朋友\N{\rEng}So this EM field is our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.93,0:24:16.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在呢\N{\rEng}But now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.85,0:24:19.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在  这个场正在分裂\N{\rEng}But now, that field is falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.95,0:24:20.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\rEng}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.05,0:24:22.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\rEng}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.49,0:24:26.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,在这里\N{\rEng}This here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.13,0:24:30.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,谁能给我找一罐空气清新剂\N{\rEng}Does somebody have a can of air freshener?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.10,0:24:37.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽量简明些\N{\rEng}Quick and dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.30,0:24:40.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,这层薄薄的皮  就是地球的表面\N{\rEng}The thin skin, that's the Earth's crust.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.24,0:24:41.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,也就是我们生活的地方\N{\rEng}That's what we live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.01,0:24:43.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,它有30英里厚\N{\rEng}It's 30 miles thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.24,0:24:47.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,果肉部分  可以称之为地幔\N{\rEng}The meat here, call it the mantle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.15,0:24:49.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,别管它们的过渡部分\N{\rEng}And forgetting all the-the funky transitions,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.02,0:24:51.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,他有2000英里厚\N{\rEng}it's 2, 000 miles thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.55,0:24:53.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个核心\N{\rEng}The core,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.02,0:24:56.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,中间突出来的部分  是最狡猾的部分\N{\rEng}the peach pit in the center... that's a tricky one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.59,0:24:57.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,它由2部分构成\N{\rEng}There's two parts
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.89,0:24:59.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,内核和外核\N{\rEng}the inner core and the outer core.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.42,0:25:00.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗\N{\rEng}Are you following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.49,0:25:01.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个内核\N{\rEng}The inner core
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.39,0:25:03.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,是…\N{\rEng}is, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.40,0:25:05.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们认为它是\N{\rEng}well, it's a big, solid chunk of iron,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.50,0:25:06.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,巨大滚烫的固体\N{\rEng}we think.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.63,0:25:08.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,它被外核所包围\N{\rEng}And that's surrounded
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.07,0:25:10.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,外核是流体形式的\N{\rEng}by the outer core, and that is liquid.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.34,0:25:11.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  但是\N{\rEng}Yes, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.70,0:25:14.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,最重要的是\N{\rEng}most importantly, this liquid is constantly spinning
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.74,0:25:15.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些流体始终是向一个方向流动的\N{\rEng}in one direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.87,0:25:19.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,上万亿吨的滚烫的溶态金属\N{\rEng}So a trillion trillion tons of hot metal
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.21,0:25:22.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,以上千英里的时速流动着  所以…\N{\rEng}spinning at a thousand miles an hour, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.68,0:25:23.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  物理学上\N{\rEng}Right, so Physics 101
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.82,0:25:26.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,热金属的快速移动会形成电磁场\N{\rEng}hot metal moving fast makes an electromagnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.35,0:25:28.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,流动的外核就是发动机\N{\rEng}This spinning liquid outer core is the engine
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.02,0:25:30.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,它驱动着地磁场\N{\rEng}that drives the EM Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.96,0:25:33.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,这也就是出问题的地方\N{\rEng}And that's where we have our problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.41,0:25:35.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个发动机停止运转了\N{\rEng}This engine has stalled.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.69,0:25:38.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,地核停止运动了\N{\rEng}The core of the Earth has stopped spinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.90,0:25:43.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会发生这种事情\N{\rEng}How could this have happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.14,0:25:45.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不知道\N{\rEng}We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.57,0:25:51.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有多少时间\N{\rEng}What's the timeline here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.21,0:25:53.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,电磁场变得越来越不稳定\N{\rEng}As the EM Field becomes more and more unstable,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.81,0:25:55.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,会附带着发生些意外\N{\rEng}we'll start seeing isolated incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.91,0:25:57.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,一架飞机从天上掉下来\N{\rEng}One plane will fall from the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.48,0:25:58.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,之后是第二架  然后…\N{\rEng}and then two, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.72,0:26:00.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,几个月之内  任何东西\N{\rEng}in a few months, anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.19,0:26:02.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,所有电子设备都将瘫痪\N{\rEng}everything electronic will be fried.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.12,0:26:03.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,空气中的静电释放\N{\rEng}Static discharges in the atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.66,0:26:05.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,会造成一场闪电风暴  每平方英里\N{\rEng}will create "super-storms" with hundreds
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.62,0:26:07.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,会遭到数百道闪电的的轰击\N{\rEng}of lightening strikes per square mile.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.23,0:26:09.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,在那之后更加糟糕\N{\rEng}After that, it gets bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.03,0:26:12.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,地球的电磁场保护我们不受\N{\rEng}The Earth's EM Field
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.96,0:26:16.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,太阳风当中致命的辐射粒子\N{\rEng}shields us from the solar winds, which are a lethal blend
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.20,0:26:20.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,和微波的伤害\N{\rEng}of radioactive particles and microwaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.17,0:26:23.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,当这层装甲崩溃了  微波辐射\N{\rEng}When that shield collapses, microwave radiation
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.68,0:26:25.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,会直接的\N{\rEng}will literally
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.11,0:26:28.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,烘烤我们的地球\N{\rEng}cook our planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.21,0:26:29.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,辛斯基博士\N{\rEng}Dr. Zimsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.45,0:26:32.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个就是太阳\N{\rEng}This is the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.65,0:26:37.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个就是地球…没有了电磁场的保护\N{\rEng}This is the Earth... without the EM Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.52,0:26:39.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,能帮个手吗\N{\rEng}Would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.24,0:26:53.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,3个月后  我们就回到石器时代了\N{\rEng}Three months, gentlemen, and we're back in the Stone Age.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.54,0:26:56.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,一年之后  磁场会崩塌\N{\rEng}A full year, the field collapses...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.88,0:26:58.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,就象这样\N{\rEng}and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.50,0:27:04.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗\N{\rEng}May l?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.94,0:27:08.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,可以扔掉了\N{\rEng}Feel free to throw up. I know I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.75,0:27:12.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么  我们该做些什么\N{\rEng}So, how do we fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.72,0:27:13.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么也做不了\N{\rEng}We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.66,0:27:14.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,在我的字典里没有不可能\N{\rEng}Not in my vocabulary.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.73,0:27:16.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,那你可能要加进去这个词了  将军\N{\rEng}Then you might want to get one of those
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.19,0:27:17.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为\N{\rEng}Word-A-Day calendars, General, because
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.86,0:27:18.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是不可能的\N{\rEng}it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.86,0:27:19.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,地核有火星那么大\N{\rEng}The core is the size of Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.00,0:27:21.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在说的是要进入行星\N{\rEng}You're talking about jump-starting a planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.80,0:27:23.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,它是滚烫的流体\N{\rEng}This is a superheated hyper-fluid
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.70,0:27:26.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,足有9 000华氏度\N{\rEng}of molten iron and nickel at 9, 000 degrees Fahrenheit,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.47,0:27:28.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,2 000英里之下  1 000英里厚\N{\rEng}2, 000 miles down, 1, 000 miles thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.87,0:27:33.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,而我们到过的最深的地方只有…7英里\N{\rEng}And the deepest we've ever been is... seven miles
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.35,0:27:34.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,用了2英寸大的钻头\N{\rEng}with a two-inch drill bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.98,0:27:36.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们能进入太空  我们当然也能…\N{\rEng}If we can go into space, we certainly...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.35,0:27:37.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,进入太空是比较简单的\N{\rEng}Well, space is easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.35,0:27:38.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为它是空的\N{\rEng}It's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.18,0:27:40.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们在说的是\N{\rEng}We're talking about millions of pounds
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.22,0:27:41.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,每平方英寸上百万磅的压力\N{\rEng}of pressure per square inch.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.72,0:27:44.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,就算我们想到了绝妙的解决方案\N{\rEng}Even if we somehow came up with a brilliant plan
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.06,0:27:47.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,来拯救地核  我们该怎么样到那里呢\N{\rEng}to fix the core, we just can't get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.03,0:27:50.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  但是…\N{\rEng}Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.33,0:27:57.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,…如果我们真的可以呢\N{\rEng}...what if we could?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.26,0:28:07.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}犹他州  盐带平地
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.42,0:28:51.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,你好  布雷兹\N{\rEng}Hello, Braz.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.86,0:28:55.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈的怎么还没死呢\N{\rEng}Why the hell aren't you dead yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.30,0:28:58.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  走这边\N{\rEng}Okay, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.80,0:29:03.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,比我预料的要好\N{\rEng}Well, that went better than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.81,0:29:06.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,布雷兹博士  我知道你认识辛斯基博士\N{\rEng}Dr. Brazzleton, I see you know Dr. Zimsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.13,0:29:09.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,20年前  他窃取了我的研究成果\N{\rEng}20 years ago, he stole my research.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.93,0:29:12.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,在那之后我们就没有接触过了\N{\rEng}After that, we-we kind of lost touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.29,0:29:13.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,那项研究也是属于我的\N{\rEng}Research that was equally mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.61,0:29:15.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,真有趣  因为我不记得有任何\N{\rEng}That's funny, I don't remember a check
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.35,0:29:16.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,专利局的证据\N{\rEng}from any of the patents.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.45,0:29:18.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了  布雷兹\N{\rEng}All right, Braz.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.04,0:29:22.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,20年的沙漠生活  使你成了个愤世嫉俗的家伙\N{\rEng}20 years in the desert makes you a prophet and a martyr.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.62,0:29:25.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们来这里是来看你那条神奇的船的\N{\rEng}Look, we're here about your legendary ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.19,0:29:29.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  那是我将高频率脉冲激光\N{\rEng}Okay, I'm combining high-frequency pulse lasers
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.26,0:29:31.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,和超声波共鸣管相结合的产物．\N{\rEng}with resonance tube ultrasonics.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.10,0:29:33.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们在探索节目看见过\N{\rEng}If you've ever seen ultrasonic waves
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.37,0:29:36.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,超声波粉碎肾结石的话\N{\rEng}break up a kidney stone on the Discovery Channel,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.43,0:29:37.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,它们的原理是一样的\N{\rEng}it's the same deal here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.60,0:29:41.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,请把头盔戴上\N{\rEng}You can... put your helmets on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.37,0:29:42.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,点火\N{\rEng}Firing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.29,0:30:34.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好  令人印象深刻\N{\rEng}Okay, I'm officially impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.89,0:30:43.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}So, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.23,0:30:44.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,看来你对引擎做了不少的改进啊\N{\rEng}So you've made some progress
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.60,0:30:47.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们承认你的贡献\N{\rEng}with the engine, we'll grant you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.27,0:30:50.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有考虑过它的外壳\N{\rEng}Have you begun to think about a shell?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.84,0:30:53.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  这个是亚历克斯．\N{\rEng}Okay, this is Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.65,0:30:56.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  亚历克斯  很好\N{\rEng}Okay, Alex. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.11,0:30:59.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,下面是混凝土块\N{\rEng}Okay, here we have a concrete block,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.28,0:31:02.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,后边是2英寸厚的钢板\N{\rEng}and in back of that, we have a two-inch steel plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.23,0:31:09.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们准备好了\N{\rEng}Okay. We're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.17,0:31:17.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后…点火\N{\rEng}And we are... firing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.69,0:31:38.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,瞧\N{\rEng}Voila!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.86,0:31:41.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,这真是…\N{\rEng}That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.36,0:31:42.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是不可思议\N{\rEng}That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.06,0:31:44.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在超低温下\N{\rEng}I combined the crystals
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.93,0:31:48.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,在结晶中混合了钨的结构\N{\rEng}in a tungsten-titanium matrix at supercool temperatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.30,0:31:51.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,产生了这种效果\N{\rEng}and that's what did the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.30,0:31:53.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,关于具体的制造工艺还是…\N{\rEng}The applications for this are just...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.77,0:31:56.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么称呼这种材料\N{\rEng}What do you call this material?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.17,0:31:58.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,哦  他的学名由37个音节构成\N{\rEng}Well, its real name has 37 syllables.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.64,0:32:00.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,我叫它Unobtainium\N{\rEng}I call it Unobtainium.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.51,0:32:02.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\bord1}{\shad1}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H111111&}{\4c&H111111&}Unobtainium\NUnobtainium?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.15,0:32:03.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEng}Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.58,0:32:06.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,Unobtainium会吸收压力和热量\N{\rEng}The Unobtainium will take the heat and the pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.28,0:32:07.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,并把它们转化为能量\N{\rEng}and transform it to energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.79,0:32:10.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,船的外壳就是由它构成的\N{\rEng}which in turn, reinforces the shell of the ship, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.89,0:32:12.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以在理论上来说  她到达得越深  所处的地方越热\N{\rEng}So the hotter and the deeper she gets,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.86,0:32:14.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,她就越强劲有力\N{\rEng}the stronger she gets... theoretically.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.41,0:32:15.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,理论上来说\N{\rEng}Theoretically?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.65,0:32:16.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,理论上  是的\N{\rEng}Theoretically, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.02,0:32:21.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是约翰逊  别理他\N{\rEng}This... is Johnson, don't mind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.43,0:32:24.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是驾驶舱的原型\N{\rEng}This is the prototype for the cockpit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.40,0:32:26.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,打断一下  布雷兹博士\N{\rEng}Excuse me, Dr. Brazzleton,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.47,0:32:28.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,这艘船什么时候可以用\N{\rEng}when do you think the ship will be operational?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.44,0:32:31.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果找到了完美的装配方案…\N{\rEng}When I get my fabrication methods perfected...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.01,0:32:34.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,12不…10年  10年就可以\N{\rEng}12... 10 years, 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.15,0:32:37.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果要让她在3个月内准备好要多少钱\N{\rEng}What would it take to get it done in three months?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.79,0:32:43.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,150亿…\N{\rEng}$15 billion. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.29,0:32:48.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能再具体核对一下吗\N{\rEng}Will you take a check?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.92,0:32:51.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不用信用卡付帐\N{\rEng}Why don't you use a credit card? You get miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.33,0:32:58.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\rEng}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.34,0:33:01.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,芬奇先生  我们是联邦调查局的  我们被授权来\N{\rEng}Mr. Finch, this is the FBl. We have a warrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.21,0:33:07.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,删除\N{\rEng}Purge!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.58,0:33:12.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,快  删除\N{\rEng}Come on, purge!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.33,0:33:27.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,FBI  不许动\N{\rEng}FBl! Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.48,0:33:38.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的．\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.78,0:33:41.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这些东西看上去像电脑\N{\rEng}I know these look like computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.41,0:33:43.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,但完全不是那么回事\N{\rEng}Totally not.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.99,0:33:45.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,希欧多尔·唐纳德·芬奇\N{\rEng}Theodore Donald Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.92,0:33:47.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,卡内基梅隆大学  麻省理工学院\N{\rEng}Carnegie-Mellon University. M.I.T.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.25,0:33:50.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,曾在SUN公司  朗讯公司  兰德公司工作过\N{\rEng}Worked at the Sun, Lucent, Rand Corp.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.76,0:33:52.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的外号是“老鼠”  叫我老鼠\N{\rEng}My handle's "Rat." Call me Rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.46,0:33:54.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,63项计算机欺诈指控\N{\rEng}63 computer fraud indictments.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.06,0:33:55.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,是64项\N{\rEng}64.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.93,0:33:57.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,2项被定罪\N{\rEng}Two convictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.06,0:34:02.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,马上就会增加到3项了\N{\rEng}This is strike three, Mr. Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.37,0:34:03.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\rEng}Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.40,0:34:05.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些人来这里不是只为了要收拾我吧\N{\rEng}You guys aren't here to whack me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.20,0:34:07.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为在那发生之前我真的想\N{\rEng}Because I was really, really hoping to have sex
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.61,0:34:08.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,有一次性经验\N{\rEng}before that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.81,0:34:12.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  FBI已经告诉我  去年\N{\rEng}Yeah. I've been told by the FBl
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.38,0:34:14.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,你毁坏了他们的数据库．\N{\rEng}whose database you crippled last year
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.61,0:34:16.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,在这一行中  你是最强的\N{\rEng}that you are the best in the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.78,0:34:18.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以我要给你一个选择\N{\rEng}So you're about to be given a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.95,0:34:20.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我说不呢\N{\rEng}What if I say no?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.08,0:34:22.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\rEng}Excuse me, but is this really
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.42,0:34:24.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,但这就是我们的最佳人选吗\N{\rEng}the best we could do?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.09,0:34:25.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是说…\N{\rEng}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.32,0:34:26.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能说多少种语言\N{\rEng}How many languages do you speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.26,0:34:27.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,5种\N{\rEng}Five, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.76,0:34:29.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  我只会一种\N{\rEng}Well, I speak one.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.63,0:34:32.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,一  零  一  零  零\N{\rEng}One, zero, one, zero, zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.36,0:34:36.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,就靠这个  我可以窃取你的金钱  你的秘密\N{\rEng}With that, I could steal your money, your secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.18,0:34:39.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的性取向  甚至你的一生\N{\rEng}your sexual fantasies, your whole life
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.64,0:34:43.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,只要我想  不论何时何地都能做到\N{\rEng}any country, any place, anytime I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.16,0:34:45.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的力量是你所无法想象的\N{\rEng}We multitask like you breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.66,0:34:48.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,即使我努力  也无法做到象你那么迟钝的思考\N{\rEng}I couldn't think as slow as you if I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.18,0:34:52.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么值得…\N{\rEng}Do you have any idea...?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.02,0:34:53.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了  好了\N{\rEng}Okay, hey. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.05,0:34:57.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,让他松口气\N{\rEng}Let's just, let's give the kid a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.37,0:35:01.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  这是电话\N{\rEng}Okay, it's a phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.05,0:35:02.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,只是个电话\N{\rEng}It's just a phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.03,0:35:10.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,老鼠  我们有大麻烦了\N{\rEng}Rat, we got a big problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.50,0:35:12.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,很多人将会死去\N{\rEng}A lot of people are going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.60,0:35:13.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要你的帮助\N{\rEng}We need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.81,0:35:14.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,哪种帮助\N{\rEng}What kind of help?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.87,0:35:16.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,信息操控\N{\rEng}Information control.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.37,0:35:18.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要你来控制因特网上的信息流动\N{\rEng}We need you to control the flow of information on the lnternet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.60,0:35:20.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在做梦吧  没有人能控制因特网\N{\rEng}You're dreaming. Nobody controls the Net.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.10,0:35:24.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,你可以吗  在有无限制的资源供应的条件下\N{\rEng}Could you... with unlimited resources?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.64,0:35:28.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是要让我黑掉整个星球\N{\rEng}You want me to hack the planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.09,0:35:31.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,他想让我黑掉整个星球\N{\rEng}He wants me to hack the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.79,0:35:38.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,用这个电话  你可以永远免费拨打\N{\rEng}You've got free long distance
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.86,0:35:41.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,长途电话了\N{\rEng}on that phone... forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.86,0:35:43.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.62,0:35:46.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,我决定了\N{\rEng}If I decide to do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.40,0:35:49.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,我需要大量的\N{\rEng}I'm going to need an unlimited supply
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.74,0:35:52.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,Xena驱动器和热水袋\N{\rEng}of Xena tapes and Hot Pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.71,0:35:54.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,热水袋\N{\rEng}Hot Pockets?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.78,0:35:56.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  这可以帮我集中精神\N{\rEng}They help me concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.51,0:35:58.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,听起来不错\N{\rEng}Sounds fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.23,0:36:10.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,切尔斯少校  他们在等你\N{\rEng}Major Childs, they're ready for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.70,0:36:15.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,切尔斯少校\N{\rEng}Major Childs
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.90,0:36:18.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,据证实\N{\rEng}a clarification
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.04,0:36:19.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,你单独提出的\N{\rEng}You and you alone were responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.90,0:36:21.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,航天飞机的降落路线\N{\rEng}for proposing the descent vectors
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.31,0:36:22.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,都是可靠的  对吗\N{\rEng}for the shuttle, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.37,0:36:23.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  将军\N{\rEng}Yes, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.74,0:36:26.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们认定这次艾德华号\N{\rEng}We have determined that the Class "A" landing mishap
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.78,0:36:28.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,A级着陆事故的起因是缘自于\N{\rEng}experienced by the Shuttle Endeavour
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.91,0:36:31.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,受地磁场干扰而造成的\N{\rEng}was caused by biased navigational data
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.55,0:36:35.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,错误的航线数据\N{\rEng}from the ground due to a brief geomagnetic disturbance.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.42,0:36:37.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,切尔斯少校  在决定降落路线\N{\rEng}Major Childs, the resourcefulness you showed
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.92,0:36:40.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,方面你显示了你的足智多谋\N{\rEng}in determining the descent vectors proved
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.26,0:36:43.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,和异常高超的航空技巧\N{\rEng}that you have exceptional navigation skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.08,0:36:45.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在太空计划和美国空军里\N{\rEng}You've brought much credit upon yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.63,0:36:48.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,为自己赢得了荣誉\N{\rEng}the space program and the United States Air Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.23,0:36:49.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜你  少校\N{\rEng}Congratulations, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.07,0:36:52.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,你被重新指派给\N{\rEng}You are reassigned
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.77,0:36:55.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾弗森指挥官和飞行主管斯蒂克利\N{\rEng}with Commander lverson and Flight Director Stickley
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.31,0:36:57.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,马上去进行一项新的任务\N{\rEng}to a new mission effective immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.91,0:36:59.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,车正等在外面\N{\rEng}Transportation is waiting outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.58,0:37:02.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运  少校\N{\rEng}Good luck and Godspeed, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.32,0:37:30.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,你确定要用这条领带\N{\rEng}Are you sure you want to wear this tie?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.51,0:37:31.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\rEng}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.51,0:37:32.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rEng}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.51,0:37:33.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是说你看上去好紧张\N{\rEng}I mean, you look so nervous about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.05,0:37:35.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,你看上去真…\N{\rEng}You look so...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.21,0:37:37.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么样啊\N{\rEng}So, how are you holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.41,0:37:38.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,哦  我很好  我很好\N{\rEng}Oh, hi. I'm good, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.85,0:37:40.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,我将要对几百人宣告\N{\rEng}I'm about to tell a couple hundred people
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.85,0:37:41.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,世界的末日就要到了\N{\rEng}the world is going to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.73,0:37:42.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的…\N{\rEng}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.75,0:37:43.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,至少我有过好日子\N{\rEng}I've had better days.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.86,0:37:45.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来还不错\N{\rEng}You look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.36,0:37:48.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  他看上去并不好\N{\rEng}No, you don't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.09,0:37:50.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么把领带系成那样\N{\rEng}Why did he touch his tie like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.09,0:37:52.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,托马斯让我和你谈谈\N{\rEng}Thomas, let me speak with you for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.13,0:37:53.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,听着  你真的不让我来做吗\N{\rEng}Listen, wouldn't you rather I did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.03,0:37:55.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是说把这份荣耀…\N{\rEng}I mean, given my reputation, I think that...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.88,0:37:58.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  不凯斯是这里的领导人\N{\rEng}No. No, Keyes is in the lead here, Zimsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.24,0:38:00.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的托马斯．但这是科学史上\N{\rEng}Yes. Thomas, this is the most important
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.24,0:38:01.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,最重要的一次行动\N{\rEng}scientific operation in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.87,0:38:04.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,以我的身份来说  我认为做这个演讲应该是我的工作\N{\rEng}And given my status, I feel that it's my job to present...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.54,0:38:06.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,＂命运计划＂才是你的工作  辛斯基\N{\rEng}Project Destiny was your job, Zimsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.51,0:38:08.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,你已经越权了\N{\rEng}And you went way beyond authorized limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.58,0:38:10.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,让我告诉你…  还是让我告诉你吧\N{\rEng}And let me tell... And let me tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.48,0:38:14.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,我真想知道  是不是＂命运＂造成了这场灾难\N{\rEng}I still, I want to know if Destiny caused this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.35,0:38:17.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不可能  但它也许是一种解决方法\N{\rEng}It's highly unlikely, but it may be the solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.36,0:38:18.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在  我还要完成检查\N{\rEng}Now, I have not finished checking...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.91,0:38:20.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\rEng}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.83,0:38:26.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴我原来的说法是错的\N{\rEng}Rebecca... I'm so glad I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.83,0:38:28.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,向右越过左边那…\N{\rEng}Right over left...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.17,0:38:29.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,不不  另外那个左边的  另外那个\N{\rEng}No, the other left, the other left.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.83,0:38:31.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,先生们．\N{\rEng}Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.17,0:38:32.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,先生们\N{\rEng}Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.54,0:38:35.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾弗森指挥官  切尔斯少校\N{\rEng}Commander lverson, Major Childs,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.61,0:38:36.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些是你的全体成员\N{\rEng}this is your crew
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.49,0:38:39.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,布雷兹博士  他了解这船\N{\rEng}Dr. Brazzleton knows the ship
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.77,0:38:42.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,辛斯基博士  精通行星学\N{\rEng}Dr. Zimsky knows the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.10,0:38:44.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,莱维柯博士  精通武器系统\N{\rEng}Dr. Leveque knows the weapons system
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.82,0:38:46.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  女士优先\N{\rEng}Excuse me, ladies first.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.39,0:38:49.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后是  凯斯博士…\N{\rEng}And Dr. Keyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.25,0:38:51.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,凯斯博士是导航系统的发明者  所以…\N{\rEng}Dr. Keyes built the navigation system, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.52,0:38:53.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,你好．我是蕾贝卡·切尔斯\N{\rEng}Hi. Rebecca Childs.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.50,0:38:54.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,鲍勃·艾弗森\N{\rEng}Bob lverson.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.31,0:38:57.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们就是你的伙伴…做什么的…\N{\rEng}These are your fellow... fellow... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.96,0:38:58.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,地心旅行\N{\rEng}Terranauts?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.03,0:39:00.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rEng}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.57,0:39:01.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都到了\N{\rEng}All this brain power over here
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.67,0:39:03.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们都在等着\N{\rEng}is starting to smell like burning batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.70,0:39:05.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们最好赶快来\N{\rEng}Y'all better come and join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.27,0:39:06.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.77,0:39:10.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是件很简单的事请  对我来说是最难的\N{\rEng}It's the simplest things that are the hardest, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.11,0:39:11.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,对  这太正式了\N{\rEng}Yeah. It's official.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.44,0:39:14.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是这次会议上资格最年轻的一个\N{\rEng}I'm the least-qualified person on this base.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.28,0:39:15.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,凯斯博士  我确定人们都在指望着你\N{\rEng}Dr. Keyes, I'm sure the people in charge
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.98,0:39:17.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们都对你充满信心\N{\rEng}have every confidence in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.25,0:39:19.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,问题就在于被指望着\N{\rEng}Well, the problem is that I'm in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.28,0:39:20.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我知道了\N{\rEng}Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.68,0:39:21.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,我能帮你吗\N{\rEng}Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.92,0:39:23.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  劳驾\N{\rEng}Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.86,0:39:28.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是个宇航员并且你也会系领带\N{\rEng}You're an astronaut, and you can tie a Windsor?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.13,0:39:31.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,有没有你做不到的事情\N{\rEng}Is there anything you can't do?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.30,0:39:34.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,就我所知  没有\N{\rEng}Not that I'm aware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.43,0:39:37.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,这真是令人不敢相信\N{\rEng}I find that incredibly intimidating.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.70,0:39:40.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  大部分人都是这样\N{\rEng}Yep. Most people do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.81,0:39:42.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里\N{\rEng}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.01,0:39:44.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.25,0:39:45.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,不客气\N{\rEng}You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.44,0:39:51.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,让我来介绍  我们项目的负责人约书亚·凯斯博士\N{\rEng}Let me introduce our project leader, Dr. Joshua Keyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.88,0:39:54.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.59,0:39:58.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好\N{\rEng}Good evening. Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.29,0:40:03.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,这看上去像一次匿名的诺贝尔颁奖会议\N{\rEng}This looks like a meeting for Nobel Prize Winners Anonymous.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.24,0:40:05.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你们都是自己领域内的佼佼者\N{\rEng}I know you are all the finest in your fields
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.69,0:40:08.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,并且是经过很长的旅途来到这里\N{\rEng}and have come a long way to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.03,0:40:13.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以  我会给出我们未来3个月的大纲\N{\rEng}So, I'll outline our program over the next three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.07,0:40:19.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,布雷兹博士会监督船的制造\N{\rEng}Dr. Brazzleton will supervise the building of a ship
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.98,0:40:22.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,用来探索我们这颗行星的核心的船\N{\rEng}which is capable of reaching the center of our planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.88,0:40:25.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,到达那里之后  它将引发一场\N{\rEng}Once there, it will deliver an explosive charge
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.45,0:40:30.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,足够巨大的爆炸  来使地核重新运动\N{\rEng}Iarge enough to restart its core.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.03,0:40:32.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,辛斯基博士会计算\N{\rEng}Dr. Zimsky will calculate
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.09,0:40:33.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,需要的爆炸当量\N{\rEng}the scale of the explosion needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.50,0:40:36.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的项目是模拟\N{\rEng}This is a program I designed to simulate the effect
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.59,0:40:38.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,在地核进行核爆炸后的结果\N{\rEng}of nuclear detonations on the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.79,0:40:42.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我的计算没有错的话  任何方向上的\N{\rEng}If my calculations are correct, a tiny nudge in any direction
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.40,0:40:44.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,轻微推动都会使地核恢复正常运转\N{\rEng}will force the core back into its normal flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.47,0:40:46.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,对行星来说“轻微推动”是什么意义\N{\rEng}What's a "tiny nudge" in planetary terms?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.34,0:40:47.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,一千兆吨当量是高还是低\N{\rEng}A thousand megatons, give or take?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.81,0:40:49.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,最多就是这么高了  因为更大的力量\N{\rEng}T ops. Because any more than that
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.37,0:40:51.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,都会使地核变得不稳定\N{\rEng}would create a core instability.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.01,0:40:54.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经制造了一些200兆吨的弹头\N{\rEng}We made a few monster warheads in the 200-megaton range.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.37,0:40:57.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,布雷兹  你认为  这艘船能成功输送这5个人吗\N{\rEng}Braz, do you think the ship can handle five of these babies?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.38,0:41:00.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我可以加大输出的功率\N{\rEng}Yeah. I can enlarge the ejection pod...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.59,0:41:03.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,请原谅  虽然我不是这方面的专家\N{\rEng}Forgive me, but, you know, I know I'm not the expert here
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.91,0:41:06.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,但如果地核过厚或者过薄又怎么样\N{\rEng}but what if the core is thicker or thinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.89,0:41:08.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  如果它不像你所认为的那样又该怎么办\N{\rEng}I mean, what if it's not what you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.06,0:41:11.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,这会影响我们爆炸的方式吗\N{\rEng}Isn't that going to affect the way the explosions are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.62,0:41:13.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊是啊\N{\rEng}Yes, yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.30,0:41:16.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果地核是乳酪做的又该怎么办\N{\rEng}And what if the core is made of cheese?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.43,0:41:18.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些全是猜想  指挥官\N{\rEng}This is all best guess, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.14,0:41:22.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,所有的科学都是最好的猜想\N{\rEng}That's all science is, is best guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.27,0:41:24.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以我的猜想就是  你不知道\N{\rEng}So my best guess is you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.38,0:41:26.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是好运  这对那些爱好和平  的人来说是个讽刺\N{\rEng}With luck, irony will break for the good guys for once,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.68,0:41:28.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,世界上最具毁灭性的武器\N{\rEng}and the world's biggest weapons of mass destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.65,0:41:31.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,会帮助我们拯救世界\N{\rEng}will help save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.28,0:41:32.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,这艘船会以一个小的\N{\rEng}The ship will be powered
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.82,0:41:34.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,试验用反应堆作动力\N{\rEng}by a small experimental nuclear reactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.53,0:41:36.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,它会被分散在6个车间里\N{\rEng}It will be divided into six compartments
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.67,0:41:38.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,就好像汽车在装配线上\N{\rEng}Iike cars on a train
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.47,0:41:41.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,机动部分在航行车间\N{\rEng}the locomotive unit, navigation department
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.29,0:41:44.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有生活部分  工程部  爆破部\N{\rEng}Iiving quarters, engineering, bomb compartment
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.50,0:41:46.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,最后的是武器控制部分\N{\rEng}and finally the weapons-control module.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.96,0:41:50.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,在斜45度角的情况下  各部分会以\N{\rEng}Up to a 45 degree angle, every compartment will be held level
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.74,0:41:52.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,螺栓型的平衡环连在一条直线上\N{\rEng}by these gyro control gimbals.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.77,0:41:55.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果有一部分坏了\N{\rEng}But if we do breach a section
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.54,0:41:58.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,隔离门会自动锁紧\N{\rEng}bulkhead doors engage automatically
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.61,0:42:01.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,封锁红色的部分  并将之排除\N{\rEng}seal off the section in red, and eject.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.91,0:42:03.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,排除是最好的选择吗\N{\rEng}Is ejection really the best option?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.86,0:42:04.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,是唯一的选择\N{\rEng}Only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.84,0:42:08.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,任何损坏的部分都会降低整体的性能\N{\rEng}Each damaged compartment degrades the entire hull.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.51,0:42:10.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,目标非常简单\N{\rEng}The objective is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.70,0:42:13.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,阻碍也很大\N{\rEng}The obstacles are gigantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.52,0:42:15.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要来自世界各地得帮助\N{\rEng}We're going to need all the help in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.36,0:42:17.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,但为了避免惊慌和混乱\N{\rEng}but if we are to avoid panic and chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.23,0:42:21.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能让外界  知道这里发生了什么事情\N{\rEng}the world at large can never know what's happening here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.53,0:42:23.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,那也正是我们的＂老鼠＂先生的世界\N{\rEng}Which is where our friend Mr. Rat comes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.77,0:42:24.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,这叫做病毒机器人\N{\rEng}It's called Virus-bot.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.77,0:42:26.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是一种能够查找文件的机器人\N{\rEng}It's a computer virus that will seek out files
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.54,0:42:29.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,可以查找任何网页上我们所指定的关键字\N{\rEng}anywhere on the Web that contain keywords that we designate
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.74,0:42:30.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,并把它们消去\N{\rEng}and wipes them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.81,0:42:34.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的功夫  真的很强啊\N{\rEng}This is my Kung-Fu, and it is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.05,0:42:37.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,在我们面前有无数的难题\N{\rEng}Meanwhile, there are a million puzzles ahead of us
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.45,0:42:39.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们只有3个月来解决他们\N{\rEng}and we have three months to solve them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.64,0:42:41.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们有一支忠诚机智的队伍\N{\rEng}We have a committed and ingenious team.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.95,0:42:44.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们拥有充足的资源\N{\rEng}We have every resource available to us
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.07,0:42:45.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们有世界上最好的\N{\rEng}and we have the best
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.83,0:42:48.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,科学与技术支持\N{\rEng}of the world's scientific and technical talents on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.21,0:42:53.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,在你们的帮助下  我们可以  我们必须  成功\N{\rEng}With your help we can, we must... succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.67,0:42:58.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,共鸣管的回馈．\N{\rEng}Feedback in the resonance tube.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.80,0:42:59.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,向我汇报  先生们\N{\rEng}T alk to me, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.57,0:43:00.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们迷路了\N{\rEng}We are losing
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.50,0:43:01.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,整体上来说\N{\rEng}structural integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.51,0:43:02.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,不行  没有回馈\N{\rEng}No, it's not feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.67,0:43:04.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,我相信  这是推进器的故障\N{\rEng}It's an impeller malfunction, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.41,0:43:06.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  绝对不会是推进器  如果真是这样…\N{\rEng}No, it's not, no. If it were an impeller malfunction...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.08,0:43:08.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,看在上帝的份上  布雷兹zleton  快打电话\N{\rEng}For God's sakes, Braz, make the call!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.28,0:43:10.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  我来打  应该是我\N{\rEng}No, I'll make the call. I should make the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.18,0:43:12.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,速度65节\N{\rEng}65 knots.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.08,0:43:13.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,深度  805 000英尺\N{\rEng}Depth, 8-5 thousand feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.02,0:43:15.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们…\N{\rEng}Look, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.69,0:43:20.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,这真是场灾难\N{\rEng}It's a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.92,0:43:22.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}任务失败
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.10,0:43:28.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们不懂＂向我汇报＂是什么意思吗  伙计们\N{\rEng}What part of "talk to me" don't you guys understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.33,0:43:30.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,第22次小组模拟\N{\rEng}For the 22nd time in a row,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.20,0:43:31.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,地球上所有人都死了\N{\rEng}everyone on Earth is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.94,0:43:34.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,安静的休息一会\N{\rEng}Let's take a little quiet time
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.91,0:43:36.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后你们要再试一次\N{\rEng}and you all are going to try this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.97,0:43:48.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\rEng}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.19,0:43:52.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个…这是我发明的\N{\rEng}It's... I invented it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.12,0:43:54.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,你就靠这个在地下驾驶\N{\rEng}It's how you're going to... going to steer underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.99,0:43:56.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个…\N{\rEng}It's, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.59,0:43:58.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,接收不太好\N{\rEng}not very good reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.33,0:44:00.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  你看见了\N{\rEng}Well, you're looking
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.71,0:44:03.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,穿过50码外3英尺厚的障碍\N{\rEng}through three feet of lead at 50 yards away, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.07,0:44:05.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,算不错的了\N{\rEng}it ain't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.40,0:44:08.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,看起来像医院的X线扫描系统\N{\rEng}It's like a CAT scan at a hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.33,0:44:11.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是这个是不一样的\N{\rEng}but it's-it's souped-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.54,0:44:12.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是为了做地底\N{\rEng}I invented it
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.91,0:44:14.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,测量才发明它的\N{\rEng}for Deep Earth surveying.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.08,0:44:16.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,政府参与进来买下了我的研究\N{\rEng}And then the government came in, bought my research
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.58,0:44:19.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,付清了我的  助学贷款  并且聘请我做顾问\N{\rEng}paid off my student loan guys and made me a consultant.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.25,0:44:21.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  这仪器非常精密\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, this is really delicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.09,0:44:22.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,它只按我的意愿来工作\N{\rEng}and I have it just the way I want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.05,0:44:25.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,让我来做\N{\rEng}So... excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.06,0:44:27.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.49,0:44:29.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,在他们的负责人辞职之后  他们就把我拉进来了\N{\rEng}Then they brought me in when the pacemakers quit
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.06,0:44:33.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,看起来我就好像个“超级男孩”\N{\rEng}and... boom you know, I'm Apocalypse Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.26,0:44:35.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,“超级男孩”\N{\rEng}Apocalypse Boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.73,0:44:38.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我有这个主题系列的T恤衫\N{\rEng}Yeah. I'm having T -shirts made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.27,0:44:41.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,那种帽子应该卖得更好吧\N{\rEng}Well, hats sell better.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.61,0:44:44.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,你看  这真的很有意思  因为…\N{\rEng}You know, it's funny, because that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.38,0:44:45.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,那个是不能移动的\N{\rEng}right where it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.04,0:44:46.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.04,0:44:48.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是令人惭愧  影像的边缘还很粗糙\N{\rEng}I'm sorry. I'm a little ragged around the edges.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.98,0:44:51.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,我正在试图令它的对焦更精确\N{\rEng}I'm just trying to get this thing to focus correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.18,0:44:52.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,这真是个很酷的想法  我想我可以…\N{\rEng}This is really cool, but can I just...?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.56,0:45:07.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,看上去好多了  确实好多了\N{\rEng}It's better. It's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.63,0:45:38.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,天啊  我讨厌这样的天空\N{\rEng}God, I hate this sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.37,0:46:22.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,一次撞毁还不能阻止你吗\N{\rEng}Crashing one ship isn't enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.80,0:46:26.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的练习会令事情事半功倍\N{\rEng}Practice makes perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.47,0:46:28.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,你可以练习所有的项目\N{\rEng}You can practice all you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.14,0:46:29.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,但这并不表示你可以担负起指挥官的责任\N{\rEng}It doesn't mean you're ready to sit in that seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.65,0:46:32.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,您是在提醒我吗  长官\N{\rEng}So you keep reminding me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.66,0:46:35.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  也许你听不进去这些话\N{\rEng}You know, I doubt you're even going to listen to this
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.26,0:46:36.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我仍然要说\N{\rEng}but I'm going to give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.69,0:46:40.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,做一个领导并不是看你有多高的技术\N{\rEng}Being a leader isn't about ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.98,0:46:42.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,它所要求的是责任感\N{\rEng}It's about responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.22,0:46:45.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了  长官\N{\rEng}Got it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.10,0:46:46.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  你没有明白\N{\rEng}No, you don't, Beck.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.01,0:46:48.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  你还并不具备令人信赖的\N{\rEng}I mean, you're not just responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.13,0:46:49.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,做出决定的能力\N{\rEng}for making good decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.28,0:46:51.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,你必须对一切不利的情况负起责任\N{\rEng}You have to be responsible for the bad ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.22,0:46:54.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,你必须时刻准备好面对最坏的情况\N{\rEng}You got to be ready to make the shitty call.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.29,0:46:56.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么认为我不行\N{\rEng}What makes you think I'm not?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.74,0:46:57.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为你太优秀了\N{\rEng}Because you're so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.15,0:47:02.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,你从来没被你所不能做到的事打败过\N{\rEng}You haven't hit anything you couldn't beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.08,0:47:02.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是说\N{\rEng}I mean, hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.68,0:47:04.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,你确是一个人演算  出了拯救航天飞机的轨道\N{\rEng}you were the one who figured out how to save the shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.20,0:47:07.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,这使得我和  航空航天局的人看起来像是废物\N{\rEng}You made me, you made the rest of NASA just look like an ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.94,0:47:12.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是天生的赢家\N{\rEng}It's just that you're used to winning...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.19,0:47:18.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,但没有经历过失败的人是当不了领导的\N{\rEng}...and you're not really a leader until you've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.96,0:47:25.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,这项计划已经花费了200亿美元\N{\rEng}$20 billion has been spent developing this system...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.10,0:47:27.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们  航空航天局里的厨子都…\N{\rEng}Oh, come on, guys, the chefs at NASA...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.89,0:47:31.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想喝酒  我需要酒\N{\rEng}I want wine! I need wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.14,0:47:34.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,那不符合营养学  在五天里…\N{\rEng}It's about nutrition. In five days, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.25,0:47:40.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是高空的静电释放\N{\rEng}That's high-level static discharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.28,0:47:44.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们应该检查一下\N{\rEng}I think we should check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.87,0:47:46.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,看上去情况不妙了\N{\rEng}This doesn't look so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.97,0:47:56.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,这种巨大的闪电风暴\N{\rEng}It's a lightning superstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.03,0:47:58.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,将在世界各地爆发\N{\rEng}Popping up all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.80,0:48:01.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,继续跟踪它的动向\N{\rEng}Got them. Tracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.74,0:48:06.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,罗马要遭殃了\N{\rEng}Rome does not look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.69,0:49:59.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,地球崩溃的速度比我们预料得更快\N{\rEng}This planet is decaying faster than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.99,0:50:01.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,这还只是个开始\N{\rEng}It's just the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.33,0:50:03.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,不久之后电磁场就会裂开\N{\rEng}Soon they'll be EM spikes
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.33,0:50:05.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,致命的微波会从缝隙间辐射进来…\N{\rEng}and microwaves will break through the weak spots and...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.03,0:50:08.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  该让这艘船出发了\N{\rEng}All right. Get this ship in the ground. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.88,0:50:16.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}南太平洋  马丽亚娜海沟
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.46,0:50:42.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是个平静的夏日啊\N{\rEng}Summer in the Pacific.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.97,0:50:44.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,对啊  世界已经天翻地覆了\N{\rEng}Yeah, the world is inside out.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.02,0:51:09.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,过一会我会挽救这一切的…\N{\rEng}I was saving this for later, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.49,0:51:11.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在要先…\N{\rEng}this is the time for...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.03,0:51:14.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,约书亚  你不会介意吧\N{\rEng}Josh, do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.30,0:51:15.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  绝对不会\N{\rEng}No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.33,0:51:18.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该给我们这个孩子取个名字\N{\rEng}We should have a name for this baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.18,0:51:19.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,它其实叫做维吉尔\N{\rEng}she's called Virgil, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.92,0:51:22.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,维吉尔就是带着我们走入地域的诗人的名字\N{\rEng}Virgil-- the poet that led our man into the depths of hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.08,0:51:23.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好  我认为这个名字很合适\N{\rEng}That's it. That's appropriate, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.34,0:51:25.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  敬我们的维吉尔\N{\rEng}Well, here's to Virgil.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.21,0:51:28.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,敬我们的地球\N{\rEng}To the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.98,0:51:29.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,-干杯  -干杯\N{\rEng}-To Virgil. -To Virgil.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.22,0:51:40.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有闪光灯  没有记者  没有人来欢送\N{\rEng}No flashbulbs, no press, nobody cheering.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.76,0:51:41.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是奇怪啊\N{\rEng}It's.... weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.66,0:51:45.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧\N{\rEng}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.28,0:52:05.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,船舱电压  TS1 3.5\N{\rEng}Cabin pressure, TSl, 3.5.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.45,0:52:06.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,完毕\N{\rEng}Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.02,0:52:09.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,发动机控制系统开启\N{\rEng}ECS cabin repress open.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.39,0:52:12.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,VLV封闭\N{\rEng}And repress VLV closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.26,0:52:13.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,完毕\N{\rEng}Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.66,0:52:14.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,固定安全阀\N{\rEng}Fluid dump valve.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.93,0:52:16.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们就要开始我们的旅程了\N{\rEng}We are about to begin our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.63,0:52:18.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,让我们进入宇宙的中心\N{\rEng}into the heart of the cosmos
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.50,0:52:20.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,到达地球的核心\N{\rEng}into the very core of our own planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.11,0:52:24.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,-在那里我们会找到…  -完毕\N{\rEng}-Where we find therein... -Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.10,0:52:26.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙万物的奥秘\N{\rEng}the secrets of the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.60,0:52:27.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\bord1}{\shad1}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H111111&}{\4c&H111111&}…3.5  PSl\N.. :3.5 PSl.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.87,0:52:29.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,…时间的秘密…\N{\rEng}...the mysteries of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.49,0:52:30.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,无线电频率锁定\N{\rEng}LM circuit lockup.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.95,0:52:33.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,-完毕  -…还有… 未来的希望\N{\rEng}-Check. -...hope for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.07,0:52:34.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,发出信号\N{\rEng}And signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.27,0:52:36.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,控制中心  这是维吉尔\N{\rEng}Deep Earth Control, this is Virgil.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.51,0:52:37.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,信号检测完毕\N{\rEng}Signal check.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.95,0:52:39.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里是控制中心\N{\rEng}This is Deep Earth Control.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.85,0:52:42.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我已经准备好这次的赌博了\N{\rEng}I have thumbs-up across the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.32,0:52:44.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,你可以启动了\N{\rEng}You are clear to initiate power-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.70,0:52:55.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,反应堆输出正常\N{\rEng}Reactor power confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.97,0:53:00.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,每分钟1 000转  我们可以倒数计时了  各就各位\N{\rEng}At 1, 000 rpm, we will countdown to launch. On your mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.24,0:53:02.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,指挥塔准备开始倒数计时\N{\rEng}Pad leader, stand by for launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.51,0:53:05.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  维吉尔\N{\rEng}All right, Virgil.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.94,0:53:07.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}系统
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.83,0:53:08.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,就位\N{\rEng}Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.65,0:53:11.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,开始倒数  10 9\N{\rEng}Gantry count. Ten, nine,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.12,0:53:15.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\bord1}{\shad1}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H111111&}{\4c&H111111&}8, 7, 6, 5, 4\Neight, seven, six, five, four,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.58,0:53:19.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\bord1}{\shad1}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H111111&}{\4c&H111111&}3, 2, 1...\Nthree, two, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.41,0:53:21.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,下潜\N{\rEng}Launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.79,0:53:55.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,500英尺\N{\rEng}500 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.79,0:53:57.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,准备启动激光系统\N{\rEng}Leveling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.77,0:54:12.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了伙计们  我们笔直前进吧\N{\rEng}Okay, guys, let's swing forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.18,0:54:20.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,800英尺\N{\rEng}800 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.85,0:54:21.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,点火  小贝\N{\rEng}Light them up, Beck.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.12,0:54:27.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,启动导航系统\N{\rEng}Gyro leveling operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.54,0:54:28.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,启动外壳损伤检查系统\N{\rEng}Hull integrity holding.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.46,0:55:03.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,我来把船体调整为15度倾角\N{\rEng}I'm going to keep her nose down about 15 degrees and...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.46,0:55:07.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的天哪\N{\rEng}Oh, my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.65,0:55:30.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,它们在向我们发信号\N{\rEng}They're singing to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.62,0:55:33.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是因为维吉尔号的共振引起的\N{\rEng}Virgil's resonance tubes are powered up,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.39,0:55:34.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以它们作出回应\N{\rEng}so they're vibrating sub sonically.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.89,0:55:36.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,实际上  是我们在向它们发信号\N{\rEng}Actually, we're singing to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.34,0:55:51.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,深度\N{\rEng}What's our depth?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.68,0:55:54.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,1600英尺  裂缝两边都有足够的空间\N{\rEng}1, 600 feet, plenty of room on both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.34,0:55:55.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,船体完好无损\N{\rEng}Hull integrity is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.45,0:55:56.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,确定\N{\rEng}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.91,0:55:57.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,增加推进器的速度\N{\rEng}Let's increase impeller speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.95,0:55:59.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们需要附加控制了\N{\rEng}I think we'll be needing additional control.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.49,0:56:05.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,史狄克  有地震信号\N{\rEng}Stick, I'm getting a seismic reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.19,0:56:06.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了\N{\rEng}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.22,0:56:09.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,T级  水下地震\N{\rEng}T -phase. Underwater earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.57,0:56:17.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,你仍然认为水下发射是个好主意吗\N{\rEng}Still think the water-launch was a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.20,0:56:20.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  是的  我选择这里是因为这里的地壳很薄\N{\rEng}Yes, yes, I chose this location because the crust is thin here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.00,0:56:23.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,地震行为越来越频繁了\N{\rEng}The downside is... there's lots of seismic activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.03,0:56:24.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,4000英尺\N{\rEng}4, 000 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.48,0:56:28.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,看到那块石头了吗\N{\rEng}You see that rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.21,0:56:29.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,好像不大妙\N{\rEng}That is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.11,0:56:38.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们无法控制方向了\N{\rEng}We're losing steering here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.31,0:56:40.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,有一股暗流在侧面推我们\N{\rEng}There's some kind of crosscurrent.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.66,0:56:42.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,14000英尺\N{\rEng}14, 000 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.64,0:56:58.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们  系好安全带\N{\rEng}Okay, guys, fasten your seat belts.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.38,0:57:01.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们要刹车了\N{\rEng}We're turning into the skid.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.79,0:57:13.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,18000英尺\N{\rEng}18, 000.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.06,0:57:15.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,18500英尺\N{\rEng}18, 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.76,0:57:17.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们的速度太快了\N{\rEng}They're going way too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.97,0:57:33.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,21000英尺\N{\rEng}21, 000 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.11,0:57:33.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们就要到达地壳了\N{\rEng}We hit the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.87,0:57:34.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们就像是高速公路上的兔子\N{\rEng}we're rabbits on the highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.99,0:57:36.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,压力  压力  压力  压力\N{\rEng}Pressure, pressure, pressure, pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.73,0:57:37.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么意思  压力\N{\rEng}What do you mean, pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.38,0:57:38.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,你好像说过这是不可能的\N{\rEng}I thought you said this thing was indestructible!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.96,0:57:40.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,压力只会让我们更强大\N{\rEng}I said the pressure makes us stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.27,0:57:42.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,压力还不够\N{\rEng}We just don't have enough of it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.76,0:57:45.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,已经25000英尺了  准备启动吧\N{\rEng}We're at 25, 000 feet. Pull out, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.63,0:57:46.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\rEng}Can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.06,0:57:47.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,-什么  -我们周围的空间还不够\N{\rEng}-What? -We're locked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.83,0:57:48.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,等到全速\N{\rEng}Go to full throttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.95,0:57:53.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,准备启动主激光器和辅助激光器\N{\rEng}Standby to engage front and lateral lasers, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.60,0:57:57.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有10秒种我们就要撞上地壳了\N{\rEng}But what if we hit bottom in ten seconds here?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.54,0:57:58.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,再等几秒钟\N{\rEng}Just give it a couple more seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.93,0:58:00.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,就发射激光\N{\rEng}The lasers will fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.27,0:58:05.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,不行  时间不够了\N{\rEng}No, there's not enough time for power-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.40,0:58:11.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,27000英尺\N{\rEng}27, 000 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.90,0:58:13.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,准备发射激光\N{\rEng}The lasers will deploy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.07,0:58:17.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,29000英尺\N{\rEng}29, 000 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.31,0:58:18.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,快点  发射\N{\rEng}Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.68,0:58:22.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,-发射  -现在\N{\rEng}-Do it! -Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.15,0:59:10.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,收到信号了\N{\rEng}And we've got a signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.60,0:59:12.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\rEng}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.55,0:59:19.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rEng}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.50,0:59:23.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,切换为电力钻探系统\N{\rEng}Switching on electron spin burst transmitters.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.49,0:59:25.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,每五分钟检测一次\N{\rEng}Plotting through lowest density material
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.92,0:59:27.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,周围环境的密度\N{\rEng}reconfiguring every five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.56,0:59:30.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,船体完好无损  反应堆工作正常\N{\rEng}Hull integrity 100%. Reactor power 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.56,0:59:32.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,武器仓完好无损\N{\rEng}All green on the bomb compartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.41,0:59:34.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,航速60节\N{\rEng}Speed is 60 knots.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.98,0:59:36.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,外面真热\N{\rEng}Hot damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.00,0:59:38.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们将在十五分钟内穿过地壳\N{\rEng}All right, we'll be through the crust in 15 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.28,0:59:39.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后进入内部\N{\rEng}and into the mantle.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.26,0:59:42.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们能挺住  24小时内到达地核\N{\rEng}24 hours to the core, and then assuming we survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.65,0:59:44.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,-假如  -没错  假如\N{\rEng}-Assuming? -Yes, assuming.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.77,0:59:48.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后还需要15小时到达里核\N{\rEng}Another 15 hours to the inner core-outer core border.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.08,0:59:50.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,干得好\N{\rEng}They're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.58,0:59:52.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,地壳只不过是一层石头\N{\rEng}The crust is just rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.35,0:59:54.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在才开始真正的挑战\N{\rEng}Now it gets interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.72,0:59:56.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,维吉尔号  检查一下周围的情况\N{\rEng}Virgil, can we get a status check?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.25,0:59:58.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们要进入地球内部了\N{\rEng}We're about to make the transition into the mantle.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.99,1:00:29.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,加油\N{\rEng}Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.65,1:00:47.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,外面的压力居然这么大\N{\rEng}Well, exterior pressure is 800, 000 pounds
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.76,1:00:48.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,每平方英寸800000磅\N{\rEng}per square inch.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.70,1:00:51.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,船体完好度100%\N{\rEng}And hull integrity is 100%.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.64,1:00:54.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,好像我们在这个星球的记忆里面\N{\rEng}It is as if we we're diving through the memories
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.98,1:00:56.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,潜水\N{\rEng}of the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.15,1:00:58.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们好像要穿过记忆\N{\rEng}But we are about to pass from memory
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.45,1:01:00.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,到达深层的疯狂地带\N{\rEng}into madness.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.38,1:01:04.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,你要一路这么念下去你那\N{\rEng}Are you going to be doing that Carl Sagan narration
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.25,1:01:05.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,蹩脚的诗吗\N{\rEng}all the way to the core?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.42,1:01:07.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,-请再说一遍  -我说\N{\rEng}-I beg your pardon? -I said...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.96,1:01:10.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,我对我的学生  我的读者有这个义务\N{\rEng}I-I have an obligation to my students, to my readers...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.23,1:01:11.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有这个义务吗\N{\rEng}An obligation to make a book deal perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.86,1:01:13.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,两本书  如果你想知道真像\N{\rEng}Two book deals, if you'd like to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.50,1:01:15.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,我以前读过最后一本书  写得不是很好\N{\rEng}I read that last book. It wasn't very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.36,1:01:16.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗  真的\N{\rEng}Oh, really? Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.55,1:01:17.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候学习读书写字的\N{\rEng}When did you learn how to read?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.89,1:01:26.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}12小时  深度700英里
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.65,1:01:39.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rEng}People
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.69,1:01:42.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,辛斯基博士和凯斯博士过来一下\N{\rEng}Drs. Zimsky and Keyes?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.86,1:01:48.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们是我们的地球物理学家\N{\rEng}You guys are our resident geophysicists.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.05,1:01:49.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,看看这是什么东西\N{\rEng}What do you make of this?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.29,1:01:53.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是一团大杂烩  由很多东西组成的\N{\rEng}The mantle is a chemical hodgepodge of... a variety of elements...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.97,1:01:58.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,说 “我不知道”\N{\rEng}Say it with me "l don't know."
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.54,1:01:59.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么  船长\N{\rEng}Well, Commander
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.78,1:02:02.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,聪明人说  当你不确定的时候  应该四处走走确定一下\N{\rEng}wise men say, "When in doubt, you should go around."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.52,1:02:03.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,不行  这东西太大了\N{\rEng}No. It's too big.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.69,1:02:04.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的转向不够快\N{\rEng}We turn too slow.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.69,1:02:07.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果有我们不能穿过的东西\N{\rEng}Anything that we can't go through
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.57,1:02:07.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,它应该是黑色的\N{\rEng}displays as black.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.99,1:02:10.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么  这到底是什么\N{\rEng}So what's... what's static?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.08,1:02:12.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么也不是\N{\rEng}It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.49,1:02:13.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\rEng}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.95,1:02:16.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么也不是\N{\rEng}It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.75,1:02:19.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里应该是空的\N{\rEng}It's empty space.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.69,1:02:22.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,我\N{\rEng}I...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.00,1:02:25.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,我忘记教电脑识别这种虚空状态了\N{\rEng}I never taught the computer how to read empty space.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.58,1:02:27.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也忘记教维吉尔号学习飞行了\N{\rEng}And I never taught Virgil how to fly.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.55,1:02:29.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\rEng}God!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.86,1:03:07.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,上帝啊\N{\rEng}dear God.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.23,1:04:01.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,赛吉  你还好吗\N{\rEng}Serge, you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.53,1:04:05.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.41,1:04:12.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,有人受伤吗\N{\rEng}Anybody hurt?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.97,1:04:14.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,我没事  你呢\N{\rEng}No. You okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.63,1:04:16.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也没事\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.06,1:04:17.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么  那是什么\N{\rEng}What's that? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.65,1:04:19.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,从冷却系统来的  快关掉\N{\rEng}From the cooling system. Shut that down.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.18,1:04:21.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,关掉\N{\rEng}Shut it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.34,1:04:22.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你要绕开她走\N{\rEng}I told you to go around her.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.59,1:04:24.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,没人听我的\N{\rEng}Nobody listens to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.01,1:04:25.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们到底在哪里\N{\rEng}Where in God's name are we?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.25,1:04:27.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的激光钻头坏了\N{\rEng}Whatever has us jammed up is inside our lasers.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.94,1:04:28.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,关掉它们吧\N{\rEng}Shut them down.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.01,1:04:34.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们哪也去不了了\N{\rEng}We're not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.75,1:04:39.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,能源关闭\N{\rEng}Powering down.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.69,1:04:48.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,约书亚  想想有什么办法把我们弄出来吗\N{\rEng}Josh, is there any other image you can pull up?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.73,1:04:49.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\rEng}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.76,1:04:53.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,无论这是什么  它已经把我们卡住了\N{\rEng}Whatever it is, it's also inside our MRl cameras.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.80,1:04:56.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们得出去一下\N{\rEng}We have to go outside.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.02,1:04:56.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.27,1:04:58.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,相信我吧  虽然我也不愿意出去\N{\rEng}Believe me, I hate to admit it
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.60,1:04:59.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想他是对的\N{\rEng}but I think he's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.77,1:05:01.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,我去  我想采集一些样品\N{\rEng}I'm coming. I want to collect samples.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.37,1:05:02.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,等等  等等\N{\rEng}Wait, hang on, hang on.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.71,1:05:03.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,等一下  首先问题是\N{\rEng}Wait, wait, the first problem is
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.91,1:05:05.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,这艘船的出口只有一个\N{\rEng}the only way out of the ship... is the way we came in,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.80,1:05:07.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是在推进器那里\N{\rEng}which is through the impeller outlet...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.77,1:05:09.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在温度足足有5000度\N{\rEng}Which is still at 5, 000 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.15,1:05:10.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是\N{\rEng}Exactly, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.67,1:05:11.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,首先要用液化氮把它冷却一下\N{\rEng}I'll just flush it with liquid nitrogen
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.99,1:05:13.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,开启冷却系统\N{\rEng}from the cooling system.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.38,1:05:15.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\rEng}Wait. The cooling system
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.59,1:05:18.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,冷却系统就是做这个用的吗\N{\rEng}that's keeping us from roasting to death in this ship?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.29,1:05:21.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  是这艘船的一部分\N{\rEng}Well, just a small part of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.13,1:05:26.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,决定一下吧\N{\rEng}Alternatives?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.66,1:05:28.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,所有人\N{\rEng}Anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.15,1:05:45.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,哇  这景象\N{\rEng}Whoa, whoa, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.68,1:05:48.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,好像全都是水晶  巨大的水晶石\N{\rEng}It's like a giant... giant crystal.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.82,1:05:50.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们到底在哪里\N{\rEng}Where the hell are we?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.79,1:05:51.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,好消息是\N{\rEng}Well, the good news is,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.79,1:05:54.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,看起来我们的工作服能够适应这里的压力\N{\rEng}it looks like the suits can take the pressure.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.26,1:05:58.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是这东西把我们的激光钻头给卡住了\N{\rEng}It's completely jammed the laser assembly.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.39,1:05:59.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,我希望\N{\rEng}We just... we got to hope,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.70,1:06:00.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们能把这东西弄出来后\N{\rEng}if we can cut it loose,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.90,1:06:02.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,-激光钻头还能工作  -小心点\N{\rEng}-they're still functional. -Careful!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.13,1:06:04.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.86,1:06:06.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,拿到了\N{\rEng}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.20,1:06:08.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,小贝  把灯打开\N{\rEng}Beck, try the lights, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.54,1:06:09.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,开灯\N{\rEng}Lighting up.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.18,1:06:17.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,-好壮观  -我的天哪\N{\rEng}-Oh, it's magnificent. -Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.33,1:06:20.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,阿拉丁藏宝的山洞\N{\rEng}Aladdin's cave.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.85,1:06:23.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,简直是水晶大峡谷\N{\rEng}It's like a crystal Grand Canyon.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.27,1:06:40.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想这些都是\N{\rEng}I think it's a geode.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.67,1:06:42.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过我不太明白\N{\rEng}But I don't understand
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.17,1:06:44.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些东西怎么会在这里\N{\rEng}how it could have survived down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.74,1:06:46.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,可能这里是钴层\N{\rEng}Cobalt shell, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.18,1:06:47.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想\N{\rEng}No. I-I mean,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.38,1:06:49.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,在这种5000度高温的环境下\N{\rEng}in a magma environment of 5, 000 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.85,1:06:51.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,一定有什么东西在保护这些水晶层\N{\rEng}Something would have to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.02,1:06:53.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,难以置信\N{\rEng}Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.15,1:06:54.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,辛斯基\N{\rEng}Zimsky.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.15,1:06:55.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\rEng}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.49,1:06:58.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们在一个宝石大厅里面\N{\rEng}We're inside a giant gem bubble
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.86,1:07:01.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,四周是钴做的茧\N{\rEng}wrapped in a cobalt cocoon
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.56,1:07:04.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,地表以下700英里\N{\rEng}700 miles below the surface of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.36,1:07:08.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕的一天\N{\rEng}Hell of a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.80,1:07:11.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,一点没错\N{\rEng}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.13,1:07:12.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,开始切割吧\N{\rEng}I'll start cutting.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.37,1:07:13.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  布雷兹\N{\rEng}Okay, Braz.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.54,1:07:14.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,我去检查一下船体\N{\rEng}I'm going to check the hull.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.54,1:07:15.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果需要帮忙就喊我一声\N{\rEng}Call me if you need me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.71,1:07:17.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.65,1:07:26.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\rEng}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.25,1:07:28.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,-辛斯基  -怎么了\N{\rEng}-Zimsky! -Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.18,1:07:29.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,辛斯基  快看\N{\rEng}Zimsky, look!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.42,1:07:30.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,紫水晶\N{\rEng}It's an amethyst.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.12,1:07:32.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\rEng}Oh, God
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.72,1:07:34.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,刚才我们把外层钴壳弄坏了\N{\rEng}we've breached the shell.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.61,1:07:51.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们  你们快回去\N{\rEng}Guys, you don't have to be here!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.71,1:07:54.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们都上船\N{\rEng}I want you back inside!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.36,1:07:55.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们确实应该上船\N{\rEng}Well, I think that means me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.95,1:07:57.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,命令就是命令\N{\rEng}Orders are orders.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.19,1:08:07.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,等等  约书亚\N{\rEng}Wait, Josh.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.56,1:08:09.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的氧气管掉了\N{\rEng}The problem is I'm losing oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.89,1:08:11.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,布雷兹  我该怎么办\N{\rEng}Braz, what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.42,1:08:12.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,快检查一下后面的氧气箱\N{\rEng}Check the feeds for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.97,1:08:15.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,快点检查一下\N{\rEng}Check the feeds for me, Josh.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.74,1:08:20.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\rEng}Quick!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.72,1:08:22.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,我正在努力\N{\rEng}I'm coming. I'm coming as fast as I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.11,1:08:23.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,快点  再这么下去\N{\rEng}Hey, guys, at this rate
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.37,1:08:25.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,三分钟后我们就要被岩浆淹没了\N{\rEng}we have three minutes before the lava gets to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.21,1:08:26.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\rEng}Come on, guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.38,1:08:27.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,加油\N{\rEng}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.32,1:08:35.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有氧气工作不了\N{\rEng}It's not going to work without oxygen!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.25,1:08:37.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,需要氧气\N{\rEng}We're losing oxygen!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.60,1:08:47.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,修好了  快点切\N{\rEng}I fixed it. Now cut!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.60,1:08:49.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,非常好  正常工作了\N{\rEng}That's good. It's working now.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.27,1:08:50.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,正常工作了\N{\rEng}It's working well now!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.63,1:08:52.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,非常好  约书亚！\N{\rEng}That's good, Josh!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.15,1:09:04.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,约书亚的生理信号不太稳定\N{\rEng}Josh's vital signs are dropping.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.37,1:09:06.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.82,1:09:13.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,赛吉！\N{\rEng}Serge!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.60,1:09:20.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,就差一点了  约书亚\N{\rEng}You're almost there, Josh.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.18,1:09:34.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,约书亚\N{\rEng}Josh!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.40,1:09:51.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,约书亚\N{\rEng}Joshua!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.66,1:09:53.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  伙计们\N{\rEng}Okay, guys,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.93,1:09:54.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,接通氧气管\N{\rEng}connect the oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.03,1:09:56.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样  行了吗\N{\rEng}Braz, you got that?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.17,1:09:57.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rEng}Yes. Connected!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.20,1:09:59.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好  我去检查一下那些激光器\N{\rEng}Good. I got to check these lasers.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.40,1:10:02.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  小贝  把它们暂时先关掉\N{\rEng}Okay, Beck, turn them over.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.11,1:10:05.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,只留下前面的如果你不介意的话\N{\rEng}Pre-lasers only, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.71,1:10:06.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,明白\N{\rEng}Initiating.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.91,1:10:09.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,干得不错\N{\rEng}This better work.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.58,1:10:12.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,要涨潮了\N{\rEng}The tide's really coming in.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.75,1:10:14.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,恩\N{\rEng}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.09,1:10:17.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们真幸运\N{\rEng}We got lucky I think we're going
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.26,1:10:18.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们就要去游泳了\N{\rEng}to swim right out of this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.86,1:10:22.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,鲍勃\N{\rEng}Bob?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.06,1:10:25.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\rEng}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.68,1:10:40.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,鲍勃\N{\rEng}Bob?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.08,1:10:47.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,鲍勃\N{\rEng}Bob...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.46,1:10:53.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,布雷兹快过来\N{\rEng}Braz, come on, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.16,1:10:55.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,来了来了\N{\rEng}Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.36,1:10:57.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,小贝  小贝\N{\rEng}Beck! Beck!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.53,1:11:00.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们就来\N{\rEng}We're coming in.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.23,1:11:02.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,快准备开船\N{\rEng}Initiate start sequence.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.73,1:11:04.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,小贝\N{\rEng}Beck
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.34,1:11:05.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,-小贝听到了吗 - 小心　　　　　　\N{\rEng}-Beck, do you hear me? -Careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.85,1:11:09.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,打开推进器\N{\rEng}Start the impellers!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.48,1:11:14.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,快开门\N{\rEng}The door, open the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.18,1:11:16.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,启动隔离门\N{\rEng}Activate bulkhead doors!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.92,1:11:19.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,快点  小贝\N{\rEng}Now, Beck!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.29,1:12:01.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样  你太虚弱了\N{\rEng}You okay? You're going to be weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.63,1:12:02.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,还好\N{\rEng}You're okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.77,1:12:07.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么\N{\rEng}So, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.77,1:12:11.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们有些好消息  并且\N{\rEng}we have some good news, and, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.30,1:12:12.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有些坏消息\N{\rEng}and we have some bad news.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.60,1:12:15.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要听好消息\N{\rEng}Good news. I'll take good news.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.40,1:12:18.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,好消息是我们还活着  还能动\N{\rEng}Well, we're alive and we're moving.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.61,1:12:20.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,这就是好消息\N{\rEng}That's g... that's good news.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.30,1:12:23.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里可真热\N{\rEng}Oh, it is hot in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.73,1:12:25.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  硝化甘油漏出去了\N{\rEng}Yeah, that nitro we flushed out
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.30,1:12:26.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的制冷系统出了问题\N{\rEng}of the cooling system, it-it's causing things
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.02,1:12:27.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,只是有点热而已\N{\rEng}just to heat up a little.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.02,1:12:28.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要回去了\N{\rEng}I'm going to go back
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.85,1:12:29.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,调整一下\N{\rEng}and just make some adjustments.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.02,1:12:31.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,让我来帮你一下\N{\rEng}I'll lend you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.12,1:12:35.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,我来检查一下你的心跳\N{\rEng}I'm going to check your heartbeat, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.49,1:12:37.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢布雷兹\N{\rEng}Thanks, Braz. Appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.78,1:12:41.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,恩  坏消息是什么\N{\rEng}So, that's the bad news?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.44,1:12:42.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,也不是真的很坏\N{\rEng}That's not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.36,1:12:46.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  艾弗森  指挥官死了\N{\rEng}No. Commander lverson died.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.02,1:12:48.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\rEng}But...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.54,1:12:50.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们活下来\N{\rEng}we're living, and he would want to...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.78,1:12:53.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是为了完成他的遗志\N{\rEng}he'd want us to complete our mission
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.31,1:12:56.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想我们都要\N{\rEng}so I think that it's important that we all...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.72,1:13:01.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,明白了\N{\rEng}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.09,1:13:04.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.46,1:13:06.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很难过\N{\rEng}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.19,1:13:12.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们为他默哀吧\N{\rEng}Let's give him a second, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.90,1:13:14.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们有这个义务\N{\rEng}He deserves that.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.47,1:13:22.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,天哪  这些东西真大\N{\rEng}Oh, God, this all just seems too big, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.18,1:13:27.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们做得事情是不可实现的\N{\rEng}I think you were attempting the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.48,1:13:29.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,试图拯救拯救这个世界  但是\N{\rEng}You were trying to save the world, and...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.68,1:13:32.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经没有退路了\N{\rEng}it's overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.28,1:13:35.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,我来这里是为了救我的妻子和两个孩子\N{\rEng}I came here to save my wife and my two children
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.85,1:13:40.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有整整60亿人  太多了\N{\rEng}and... six billion lives it's too much.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.19,1:13:42.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只希望  我能够\N{\rEng}I just hope I'm-I'm smart enough
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.23,1:13:44.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,对她们三个尽到我的责任\N{\rEng}and brave enough to save three.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.46,1:13:48.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,干得好  约书亚  非常好\N{\rEng}You did a nice job, Joshua. Very nice. Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.13,1:13:50.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,你也不错\N{\rEng}You'd have done the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.84,1:13:51.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,呵呵  也许吧\N{\rEng}Well, maybe, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.71,1:14:06.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  谁在开船\N{\rEng}Hey... who's steering the ship?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.15,1:14:08.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在是自动导航\N{\rEng}Video screen autopilot.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.82,1:14:10.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,我希望它能分清路\N{\rEng}I hope he knows the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.39,1:14:14.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,希望如此\N{\rEng}You and me both.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.53,1:14:19.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,你真的是个大学教授\N{\rEng}So... you're really a college professor?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.54,1:14:20.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不是CIA\N{\rEng}You're not from the ClA
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.50,1:14:24.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,或者NSA或者随便其他什么组织的人\N{\rEng}or the NSA or any of those three-letter places?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.54,1:14:27.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  我就是一个大学教授\N{\rEng}No. I am a boring college professor.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.27,1:14:32.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,真不是地方\N{\rEng}Wrong place, wrong place.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.38,1:14:36.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是我见过最勇敢的事情了\N{\rEng}That was the bravest thing I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.21,1:14:37.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只是\N{\rEng}Well, I just, I just...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.72,1:14:40.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗  刚才没有氧气的时候\N{\rEng}Listen, the lack of oxygen
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.01,1:14:41.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,我简直像个小女孩一样软弱无力\N{\rEng}kept me from weeping like a little girl
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.72,1:14:45.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,在危险面前我总是很软弱\N{\rEng}as is my custom in dangerous situations.
