Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.63,1:14:57.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们  我们已经到了地核表面了\N{\rEng}Hey, guys, we're close to the mantle core interface.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.54,1:14:58.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里\N{\rEng}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.67,1:15:01.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,启动操作已经确认\N{\rEng}Key's in, Dr. Brazzleton.
