Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.02,1:15:06.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,号码是  0—1—3－1－9－9－5\N{\rEng}Okay, the code... 0-1-3-1-9-9-5.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.58,1:15:08.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,完美的武器控制\N{\rEng}...Iuxurious, beautiful weapons control...
