Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.44,1:15:36.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好  把它们放好\N{\rEng}All right, now let's put them to bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.61,1:15:41.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,辛斯基  能来一下吗\N{\rEng}Zimsky, could you please come up here for a second?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.21,1:15:42.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,来了\N{\rEng}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.51,1:15:44.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,照理说我们是不能通过黑色区域的\N{\rEng}We're not supposed to go through anything black.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.05,1:15:46.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么就不要在那里走好了\N{\rEng}Yes, so please don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.25,1:15:47.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么？\N{\rEng}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.99,1:15:51.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,到处都是\N{\rEng}They're scattered everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.16,1:15:56.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,天哪  这是钻石\N{\rEng}Oh, my God! They're diamonds!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.52,1:15:59.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了！\N{\rEng}Great.
