Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.75,1:16:03.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,很可能会有碰撞发生\N{\rEng}We're on a collision course here.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.81,1:16:11.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  小心点\N{\rEng}All rightie. Careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.38,1:16:18.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们  我们在躲避这些像暗礁一样的钻石\N{\rEng}Guys, we're dodging diamonds the size of Cape Cod
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.22,1:16:19.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,小心点\N{\rEng}so bear with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.98,1:16:21.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,还是不够敏捷\N{\rEng}Not exactly nimble here.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.85,1:16:23.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,钻石  我也想要\N{\rEng}Diamonds? I want some.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.35,1:16:24.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,我能帮什么忙吗\N{\rEng}Can I help?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.28,1:16:47.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\rEng}Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.91,1:16:48.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\rEng}Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.88,1:16:53.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,没关系  没关系\N{\rEng}Okay. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.92,1:16:58.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,恩  看起来好像搞定了\N{\rEng}Okay, it looks like we're in the clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.26,1:17:05.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,机舱受损\N{\rEng}Breach!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.03,1:17:08.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,快从武器控制室出来！\N{\rEng}Guys! Weapons control, get out!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.70,1:17:09.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,快出来\N{\rEng}Get out now!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.14,1:17:22.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,赛吉\N{\rEng}Serge!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.22,1:17:26.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,赛吉  你在干什么\N{\rEng}Serge! What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.71,1:17:28.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\rEng}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.45,1:17:29.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的笔记本\N{\rEng}My notebook!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.44,1:17:31.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\rEng}Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.49,1:17:35.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,赛吉\N{\rEng}Serge!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.17,1:17:44.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,带上　　　约书亚\N{\rEng}T ake the time reg, Joshua!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.50,1:17:46.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,赛吉  快点\N{\rEng}Come on Serge! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.14,1:17:47.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的笔记本  不能丢掉\N{\rEng}My notes! You'll need them!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.07,1:17:48.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.07,1:17:51.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,看在上帝的份上  快走\N{\rEng}God, no, Serge!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.34,1:17:52.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\rEng}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.68,1:17:54.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,赛吉  不  不要去\N{\rEng}Serge, come on! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.58,1:17:55.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,赛吉\N{\rEng}Serge!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.58,1:17:56.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\rEng}Come on, man!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.88,1:18:00.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,-扔掉那破盒子 -我们需要它　\N{\rEng}-Leave the box! -We need the box!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.79,1:18:02.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们能救他  我们能把他救出来\N{\rEng}We can get him! We can get him out!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.59,1:18:06.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住  赛吉\N{\rEng}Hold on, Serge!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.47,1:18:20.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,小贝  小贝\N{\rEng}Beck! Beck!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.47,1:18:23.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,不要启动自动分离系统！\N{\rEng}Override the ejection system!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.24,1:18:26.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,小贝  不！  如果有一段损坏\N{\rEng}Beck, no! One damaged compartment
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.18,1:18:27.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,整艘船都会遭殃\N{\rEng}threatens the whole ship!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.28,1:18:30.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,小贝  小贝\N{\rEng}Beck! Beck!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.72,1:18:34.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,不要启动自动分离系统！\N{\rEng}Override the ejection system!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.16,1:18:41.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,赛吉  我们都在这\N{\rEng}Serge, we're right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.21,1:18:43.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们会永远记着你\N{\rEng}We're not going to forget about you, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.26,1:18:44.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,-约书亚能听到吗　　 -赛吉  赛吉\N{\rEng}-Josh, can you hear me? -Serge! Serge...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.66,1:18:46.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,伙计  仔细看着监视器\N{\rEng}Hey, buddy, look in your monitor right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.20,1:18:47.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,赛吉  好好看着你的监视器\N{\rEng}Serge, look in your monitor.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.27,1:18:49.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在这  赛吉\N{\rEng}I'm right here. Serge...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.17,1:18:51.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,约书亚  我看不到你\N{\rEng}Josh, I can't see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.67,1:18:54.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,布雷兹正在试图开门 坚持住\N{\rEng}Braz is going to override the doors manually, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.08,1:18:55.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在努力  布雷兹  还要多长时间\N{\rEng}We're working on it right now. Braz, how long?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.96,1:18:58.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,我尽快\N{\rEng}Going as fast as I can, Fast as I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.74,1:19:01.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,- 刚才吓死我了　 - 我们现在都在这\N{\rEng}-Okay, I'm scared. -We're going right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.95,1:19:03.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,不应该是\N{\rEng}Shouldn't be two seconds, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.35,1:19:04.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,约书亚\N{\rEng}Josh!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.42,1:19:07.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,小贝  中止自动分离系统！\N{\rEng}Beck, override the ejection systems, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.22,1:19:09.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,真糟糕  她好像听不到我\N{\rEng}Damn. I don't think Beck can hear me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.85,1:19:11.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,赛吉  看着我  赛吉\N{\rEng}Serge, look at me now. Serge!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.96,1:19:13.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们安全了  赛吉\N{\rEng}Serge, we're right here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.69,1:19:15.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不会丢下你不管的  伙计\N{\rEng}We're not going to forget about you, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.43,1:19:16.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会把你救出去的\N{\rEng}I'm going to get you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.86,1:19:18.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我正在努力\N{\rEng}We're working on it, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.23,1:19:21.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,别丢下我\N{\rEng}Stay with me here. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.30,1:19:22.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,实在没办法了\N{\rEng}I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.83,1:19:24.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在能听到我了吗  很好  是我\N{\rEng}Can you hear me now? All right, here I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.24,1:19:25.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你走的\N{\rEng}I'm not going to let you go, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.37,1:19:27.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你走的  你知道吗\N{\rEng}I'm not going to let you go, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.91,1:19:31.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,留下来\N{\rEng}Stay with me here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.31,1:19:32.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要去巴黎\N{\rEng}I'm going to come to Paris
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.64,1:19:34.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们一定能从这里脱身\N{\rEng}and we'll go out, all right? After this.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.71,1:19:37.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,等到这一切都结束了\N{\rEng}After this is all said and done, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.53,1:19:39.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,赛吉\N{\rEng}Serge!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.18,1:19:41.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,赛吉  赛吉\N{\rEng}Serge! Serge!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.55,1:19:44.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,赛吉\N{\rEng}Serge!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.26,1:19:46.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,赛吉\N{\rEng}Serge!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.65,1:20:22.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.38,1:20:41.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,你没听见我说什么吗？\N{\rEng}Did you reset the overrides?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.51,1:20:45.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,不行  我不能这么做\N{\rEng}I never pushed them.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.33,1:20:48.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,是你让他死的\N{\rEng}You let him die.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.46,1:20:52.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,说实话  你真的想知道\N{\rEng}Actually, you really want to know?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.82,1:20:54.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,我已经杀了他两次\N{\rEng}I killed him twice.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.39,1:20:55.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,第一次是我撞上那钻石的时候\N{\rEng}First when I hit the diamond,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.49,1:20:56.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后我没有中止自动分离系统\N{\rEng}and then when I didn't hit the override.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.99,1:20:59.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我会为我所做的一切感到羞愧吗\N{\rEng}Do you want me to feel any worse about that than I already do?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.56,1:21:00.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\rEng}It's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.67,1:21:01.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,你这么自鸣得意做什么\N{\rEng}Why are you being so smug about that?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.10,1:21:03.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能做这个决定吗\N{\rEng}Could you have made the decision?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.50,1:21:04.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,-能　 -你能吗\N{\rEng}-Yes. -Could you?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.50,1:21:05.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,我能\N{\rEng}Yes, I could've.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.60,1:21:06.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你打开了开关\N{\rEng}If you would've hit that switch,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.70,1:21:07.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就能把他弄出来\N{\rEng}I could've got him outta there!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.83,1:21:09.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,听到了没有\N{\rEng}I was yelling for you!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.68,1:21:15.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,看看这个\N{\rEng}Take it and look at it!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.48,1:21:18.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,我离他只有两英寸\N{\rEng}I was two inches from him!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.18,1:21:19.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,两英寸\N{\rEng}I was two inches,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.85,1:21:21.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也告诉过你把门开开\N{\rEng}and I told you to put the door up
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.45,1:21:22.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,然而你没有\N{\rEng}and you didn't!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.46,1:21:24.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知不知道\N{\rEng}I was screaming for you!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.26,1:21:26.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么这么做\N{\rEng}Why didn't you do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.86,1:21:29.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为我决定这么做\N{\rEng}Because I had to make that decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.46,1:21:31.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是上天注定的\N{\rEng}Fate or God...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.20,1:21:32.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.26,1:21:34.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,你少给我胡扯什么上帝\N{\rEng}Damn it! You leave God out of this!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.17,1:21:36.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,赛吉死了  然而我们仍然要完成我们的任务\N{\rEng}Serge died so that we could complete our job.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.50,1:21:37.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  任务  拯救世界\N{\rEng}Oh, that's right, the job of saving the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.10,1:21:42.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是整个世界约书亚  而是赛吉的家人\N{\rEng}Not the whole world, Josh! Just three of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.69,1:22:31.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}35小时  深度1900英里
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.22,1:22:35.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,维吉尔号  你们已经接近外核了\N{\rEng}Virgil, you are approaching core interface.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.03,1:22:37.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样  有信心吗\N{\rEng}Are you good to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.30,1:22:38.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,约书亚\N{\rEng}Josh?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.56,1:22:40.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,约书亚  能听到我吗\N{\rEng}Josh, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.17,1:22:45.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,约书亚  听到了吗\N{\rEng}Josh, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.37,1:22:52.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,随时待命  史迪克\N{\rEng}Ready as we'll ever be, Stick.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.64,1:22:55.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,凯斯 博士\N{\rEng}Dr. Keyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.08,1:22:57.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在这\N{\rEng}Right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.82,1:23:03.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,深入地心  我们状态很好  信心十足\N{\rEng}Deep Earth, we are green and good to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.73,1:23:44.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,要加速了\N{\rEng}We just got a huge speed jump.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.03,1:23:46.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在的速度是95节\N{\rEng}We're at 95 knots.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.00,1:23:48.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,110节\N{\rEng}110.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.37,1:23:50.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\bord1}{\shad1}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H111111&}{\4c&H111111&}130  140\N130... 140.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.07,1:23:53.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,地核和我们预料的不太一样\N{\rEng}Our speed's jumped because the density of the core
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.37,1:23:54.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们的速度不太正常\N{\rEng}is different than our estimates.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.91,1:23:56.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,地核的密度比我们想象的要小\N{\rEng}It's lighter than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.67,1:23:57.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,情况比预料的要好\N{\rEng}So much for best guesses.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.78,1:23:58.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,对此我很满意\N{\rEng}I'm fine with this.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.84,1:23:59.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去  我们  什么\N{\rEng}At this rate, we'll, what
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.88,1:24:03.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,五小时内到达里核\N{\rEng}hit the inner core in a little over five hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.44,1:24:04.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,好运气终于来了\N{\rEng}I think we finally bought some luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.78,1:24:05.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,布雷兹\N{\rEng}Braz.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.18,1:24:06.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,-什么事  -你可以\N{\rEng}-Yeah. -Would you please
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.25,1:24:08.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,帮忙重新计算一下地核密度\N{\rEng}punch the new core density into the equations
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.19,1:24:09.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,对爆破的影响吗\N{\rEng}for the nuclear detonation?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.96,1:24:13.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}下载假定情况…完成
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.13,1:24:16.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,这应该够了\N{\rEng}Please tell me this is enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.03,1:24:23.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.40,1:24:26.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是说我们那1000兆吨级的核弹\N{\rEng}You're telling me the 1, 000 megatons of nuclear warheads
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.90,1:24:28.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,还是不能起到作用\N{\rEng}we hauled down here isn't going to cut it?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.81,1:24:32.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是  地核的密度比我们预想的要小\N{\rEng}No. This core material is too thin.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.38,1:24:33.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,-什么  -所以爆炸的\N{\rEng}-What? -The energy waves from
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.88,1:24:34.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,冲击波传播的一定不会很远\N{\rEng}the explosion won't spread far enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.05,1:24:36.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,根本不可能起到什么作用\N{\rEng}They'll just bleed away into nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.65,1:24:43.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,也对\N{\rEng}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.39,1:24:45.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们回去  我们回去\N{\rEng}We go home. We go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.92,1:24:47.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,-回去 -什么\N{\rEng}-Home? -What?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.89,1:24:49.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,指挥官死了\N{\rEng}Our Commander is dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.59,1:24:51.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,武器专家也死了\N{\rEng}Our weapons specialist is dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.20,1:24:52.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,武器控制系统也坏了\N{\rEng}Our weapons control systems are gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.06,1:24:55.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们甚至都不能确定  核弹是否还能正常工作\N{\rEng}We don't know whether we can arm the nuclear devices,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.77,1:24:58.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,并且我们的修复地心计划  也出了问题  所以\N{\rEng}and our plan to fix the core no longer works. So...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.40,1:24:59.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经失败了\N{\rEng}we have failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.44,1:25:00.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们还没有败\N{\rEng}We have not failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.64,1:25:02.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经败了  回去吧\N{\rEng}We have failed, and we go home
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.84,1:25:05.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有别的方法\N{\rEng}and we go to the alternative.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.24,1:25:07.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么方法  你在说什么\N{\rEng}What alternative? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.05,1:25:09.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,将军  我是康拉德·辛斯基博士\N{\rEng}General, this is Dr. Conrad Zimsky.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.81,1:25:10.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,启动“命运”计划\N{\rEng}Destiny is a go.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.82,1:25:11.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,重复\N{\rEng}Repeat.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.82,1:25:13.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,启动“命运”计划\N{\rEng}Destiny is a go.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.68,1:25:14.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,这下糟了\N{\rEng}Damn.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.36,1:25:22.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,我需要知道一切与我任务有关的资讯\N{\rEng}I need to know everything to do my job.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.66,1:25:24.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,你没必要知道\N{\rEng}You don't have to know this.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.03,1:25:26.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,将军  确保这项任务\N{\rEng}General, it is my job
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.56,1:25:29.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,的顺利执行是我的工作\N{\rEng}to ensure the safety of this mission.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.37,1:25:31.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,任何对任务有影响的事情我都需要知道\N{\rEng}Anything that affects it is my business.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.80,1:25:33.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个“命运”计划到底是什么\N{\rEng}Now what the hell is Destiny?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.60,1:25:35.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,一种装置\N{\rEng}It's a device.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.61,1:25:41.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,深层地震引发系统  D—E—S—T—I—N—Y\N{\rEng}Deep Earth Seismic T rigger lnitiative, DEST -INI. Destiny.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.68,1:25:43.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想现在我们\N{\rEng}We had reason to believe
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.15,1:25:45.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,的首要任务是让我们的炸弹\N{\rEng}that our enemies were building a weapon
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.42,1:25:47.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,能够产生足够强的力量\N{\rEng}that could generate targeted seismic events.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.39,1:25:51.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,强到能够使这里整个区域发生\N{\rEng}They would be able to create massive earthquakes
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.69,1:25:52.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,超大规模的地震\N{\rEng}under our territory.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.69,1:25:54.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,谁能做到\N{\rEng}No way of telling who did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.69,1:25:55.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\rEng}So?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.29,1:25:57.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以  我们自己来\N{\rEng}So... we built one, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.90,1:25:58.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,M．A．D．\N{\rEng}M.A.D.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.06,1:26:01.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,互动破坏系统\N{\rEng}Mutually Assured Destruction.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.71,1:26:03.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好  名字不错\N{\rEng}A perfect acronym if ever there was one.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.68,1:26:04.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,很美\N{\rEng}Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.47,1:26:05.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们做出了原型\N{\rEng}They built it first.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.57,1:26:06.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,我将它改进的更完美\N{\rEng}I built it better.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.57,1:26:07.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以用\N{\rEng}I beamed high-powered
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.04,1:26:11.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,高压电能产生定向的冲击波\N{\rEng}electromagnetic energy waves down Deep Earth fault lines, and, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.95,1:26:13.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,辛斯基你怎么能这么想\N{\rEng}Zimsky, what makes you think
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.11,1:26:15.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得“命运”的威力真的能深入地核吗\N{\rEng}that Destiny would even touch the core?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.48,1:26:17.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,确实有这个威力\N{\rEng}'Cause it already did.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.18,1:26:21.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,这不是意外\N{\rEng}This isn't a fluke.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.89,1:26:22.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,这场灾难就是“命运”造成的\N{\rEng}We killed the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.99,1:26:24.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,你一直在说地核太大了\N{\rEng}You keep saying that the core is too big
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.86,1:26:26.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,很容易对核爆作出反应\N{\rEng}to be affected by anything short of nukes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.86,1:26:28.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,-那么  -地核就象是一部引擎\N{\rEng}-So... -The core is an engine.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.67,1:26:29.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,就算把一个小扳手扔进引擎里\N{\rEng}Throw a small wrench into a big engine,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.76,1:26:31.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,你也能把它弄停\N{\rEng}you can still stall it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.00,1:26:35.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,总部  维吉尔号呼叫\N{\rEng}Deep Earth, this is Virgil.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.67,1:26:40.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要完整的“命运”计划细节\N{\rEng}We require clarification on the status of Project Destiny.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.34,1:26:41.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我们对此一无所知\N{\rEng}Why weren't we notified of this, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.01,1:26:43.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为你们根本不需要\N{\rEng}Because you didn't need to know, Major.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.11,1:26:46.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你对此不满\N{\rEng}Now you may not like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.88,1:26:48.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也一样不喜欢\N{\rEng}I may not like it either.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.21,1:26:50.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的工作  我这么做是为了国家\N{\rEng}But it's my job, and I do it for my country,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.38,1:26:53.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,并且如果我们不开发这些武器  别人就可能会开发\N{\rEng}and if we don't develop these devices, someone worse will
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.32,1:26:54.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,并且用来对付我们\N{\rEng}and they will use them against us.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.05,1:26:56.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是你已经知道情况了\N{\rEng}but you have my word.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.72,1:26:59.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,任何人都没有权力知道这些  谁都不行\N{\rEng}No one in this administration no one,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.72,1:27:02.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何都不行\N{\rEng}had any idea that this could happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.23,1:27:05.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么这个“命运”就是你的备用计划了\N{\rEng}So the device that killed the planet is your backup plan?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.28,1:27:08.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,触电能够让心脏停止跳动\N{\rEng}An electric shock can stop a heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.29,1:27:10.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,当然也能让心脏启跳\N{\rEng}It can certainly restart one.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.14,1:27:12.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,“命运”能够起到作用\N{\rEng}Destiny will work.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.06,1:27:12.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,一定会的\N{\rEng}It has to.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.81,1:27:14.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,不会的 不可能起作用\N{\rEng}No, it won't work.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.21,1:27:15.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,地核已经出现异常\N{\rEng}If you fire that thing again
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.60,1:27:17.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,你再发射那东西  你会毁了地核\N{\rEng}with the core already stalled, it'll terminally destabilize it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.87,1:27:19.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  我们要冒很大的风险\N{\rEng}Yes, granted-- there is a marginal risk involved,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.74,1:27:20.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是事情已经到了这个地步\N{\rEng}but given the circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.05,1:27:22.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们已经别无选择\N{\rEng}I hardly see that there's an alternative.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.61,1:27:23.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  辛斯基  听我说\N{\rEng}No, Zimsky, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.61,1:27:25.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,地球上的每座火山都会爆发\N{\rEng}Every volcano on the planet will blow.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.18,1:27:27.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,那时的地震足够把任何东西撕成碎片\N{\rEng}There'll be earthquakes big enough to rip us to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.85,1:27:28.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,-凯斯博士  -什么　　　　\N{\rEng}-Dr. Keyes. -What?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.85,1:27:30.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在只有这个办法了\N{\rEng}I'm afraid it's all we've got.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.69,1:27:32.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在总统已经下达了命令\N{\rEng}Now, I have orders from the president.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.99,1:27:34.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,回来吧 维吉尔号\N{\rEng}Come home, Virgil.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.12,1:27:35.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们要执行B计划了\N{\rEng}We go to plan B.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.13,1:27:36.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么为什么不试试C计划\N{\rEng}Well, what about plan C?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.86,1:27:37.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEng}What? What?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.86,1:27:38.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,C计划\N{\rEng}Well, plan C.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.06,1:27:40.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们接着干\N{\rEng}We continue on.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.28,1:27:42.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,重新让地核活动起来\N{\rEng}We restart the core... somehow.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.77,1:27:45.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你发射“命运”  我们就不干了\N{\rEng}We don't do it, you fire Destiny.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.47,1:27:46.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,我没有时间等你们撤退\N{\rEng}I can't wait for you to get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.94,1:27:48.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么就先等等  如果我们失败了再发射\N{\rEng}Then don't. We fail, fire Destiny.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.84,1:27:50.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,这太可笑了吧\N{\rEng}Oh, come on! That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.21,1:27:50.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们有什么选择吗\N{\rEng}What choice do we have,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.94,1:27:51.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,-辛斯基  -你在开玩笑吗\N{\rEng}-Zimsky? -Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.08,1:27:53.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们现在发射那东西\N{\rEng}If they set that thing off,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.28,1:27:54.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,冲击波会把我们撕碎\N{\rEng}the shock waves will wipe us out!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.71,1:27:56.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们现在就撤  也许还能回的去\N{\rEng}We'll be lucky to get back if we turn back right now!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.01,1:27:59.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,维吉尔号  给我听着  我们必须发射“命运”\N{\rEng}Virgil, I'm telling you right now, we will fire Destiny,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.05,1:28:02.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,并且我们会尽快发射\N{\rEng}and we need to do so as quickly as possible,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.19,1:28:03.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你还不赶快回来\N{\rEng}and if you're still there,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.69,1:28:05.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们就完了\N{\rEng}you will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.79,1:28:07.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,蕾贝卡\N{\rEng}Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.59,1:28:09.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,请不要逼我这么做\N{\rEng}Please don't make me have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.50,1:28:16.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,C计划\N{\rEng}Plan C.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.50,1:28:21.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,该下决定了  指挥官\N{\rEng}It's your call, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.98,1:28:30.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,少数服从多数\N{\rEng}Majority decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.31,1:28:32.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们继续\N{\rEng}We're going in.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.98,1:28:34.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  长官\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.15,1:28:39.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么  你们这些傻瓜疯了吗\N{\rEng}Oh, come on, you're a bunch of suicidal morons!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.34,1:28:40.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了\N{\rEng}What are you, crazy?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.69,1:28:43.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,C计划  重新启动地核\N{\rEng}Plan C? Restart the core "somehow"?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.62,1:28:44.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是个好主意\N{\rEng}Oh, that's a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.93,1:28:45.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们真是才华横溢\N{\rEng}That's a brilliant idea!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.93,1:28:46.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,真难以置信\N{\rEng}I can't believe I'm stuck
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.60,1:28:48.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,这么一艘破船  你们这一群疯子\N{\rEng}in this floating septic tank with you lunatics!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.70,1:28:50.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们是没什么可失去的\N{\rEng}You may have nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.20,1:28:51.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们什么都没有\N{\rEng}You may have nothing to lose!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.20,1:28:52.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们什么都没有\N{\rEng}You may have nothing to lose
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.20,1:28:53.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是我还不想死\N{\rEng}but I have my life to lose,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.20,1:28:54.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢  你们赶快给我醒过来\N{\rEng}thank you very much while you're up!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.47,1:28:55.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,好好想想\N{\rEng}Now turn it around!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.47,1:28:57.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,他让我们回去  那么我们回去好了\N{\rEng}He told us to go back and we're going back!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.33,1:28:59.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想做英雄吗  你想做烈士\N{\rEng}Why? You want to be a hero? You want to be a martyr?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.18,1:29:01.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想干什么  你已经疯了\N{\rEng}What do you want to be? You're out of your mind!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.08,1:29:02.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,好好想想  谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you! Turn it around!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.42,1:29:03.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,-不  -辛斯基\N{\rEng}-No! -Zimsky.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.15,1:29:10.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\rEng}You, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.86,1:29:18.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,这艘船一点都不愚蠢\N{\rEng}It's not a stupid ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.10,1:29:21.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉\N{\rEng}I had to.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.84,1:29:27.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,以前也发生过这种事情\N{\rEng}It had to happen sometime.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.68,1:29:36.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,报告情况  怎么回事\N{\rEng}Status! What is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.75,1:29:38.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个磁场监控站\N{\rEng}It's the EM monitoring station.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.52,1:29:39.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,负责监控\N{\rEng}It's the one that
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.52,1:29:40.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,磁场的状态\N{\rEng}tracks EM pulses.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.68,1:29:42.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的天哪\N{\rEng}God, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.26,1:29:47.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事  “老鼠”先生\N{\rEng}Just talk, Mr. Rat.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.42,1:29:48.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.43,1:29:49.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们干得不错\N{\rEng}That's a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.06,1:29:52.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,还记得约书亚说的那些\N{\rEng}Remember those invisible microwaves
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.66,1:29:54.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,微冲击波吗\N{\rEng}that Josh was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.83,1:29:57.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,它们已经漏进来了\N{\rEng}Well, they just found a hole.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.03,1:29:59.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}已侦测电磁摧毁处
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.67,1:30:39.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是  这里又塞车了\N{\rEng}No, it's a parking lot out here...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.06,1:30:55.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的天哪\N{\rEng}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.03,1:31:30.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\rEng}And now with this
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.49,1:31:31.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,重大灾难新闻报道\N{\rEng}horrific breaking news,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.96,1:31:35.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,旧金山遭遇了大规模自然灾害\N{\rEng}we go live to San Francisco, where Leo Jacks has the story.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.70,1:31:37.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  克莱尔  确实难以置信\N{\rEng}Yes, Claire, it's hard to believe
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.84,1:31:40.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,今天半个旧金山已经毁了\N{\rEng}that half of San Francisco is in ruins today
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.30,1:31:42.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,完全毁灭  而我们对此无计可施\N{\rEng}following the most devastating and the most baffling
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.64,1:31:46.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,回溯我们的过去\N{\rEng}event in our nation's history.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.31,1:31:48.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,情况还从来没有这么糟过\N{\rEng}It's-it's a horrific situation here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.25,1:31:49.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,数千人死亡\N{\rEng}Thousands are dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.38,1:31:50.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,更多的人失踪\N{\rEng}Many are missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.55,1:31:52.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,看看这些旅馆  医院\N{\rEng}It's-it's hotels, hospitals.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.52,1:31:54.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,开启能源监视系统\N{\rEng}Bring up the power grid.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.52,1:31:59.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,整个西海岸线都处于危险中\N{\rEng}The whole West Coast is out.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.72,1:32:03.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果洛杉矶山脉爆发\N{\rEng}That means we're going to have to suck up just about every drop
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.43,1:32:04.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们对那些岩浆和高温气体束手无策\N{\rEng}of juice east of the Rockies
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.86,1:32:06.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,准备发射“命运”\N{\rEng}to fire Destiny.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.20,1:32:09.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,磁场再次异常  我们的能源快要不够了\N{\rEng}Another EM spike, we're not going to have enough power.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.10,1:32:13.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,将军  你必须多给他们点时间\N{\rEng}General, you have got to give them more time.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.80,1:32:15.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,已经没有时间了\N{\rEng}There is no more time.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.14,1:32:16.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,将军  准备完毕\N{\rEng}Colonel, call Destiny.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.47,1:32:17.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要向国防部提交\N{\rEng}I am launching a formal complaint
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.98,1:32:20.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,正式的抗议书了\N{\rEng}against you with the Department of Defense.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.54,1:32:21.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,“老鼠”呼叫约书亚\N{\rEng}Rat to Josh.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.55,1:32:22.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,继续“老鼠”\N{\rEng}Go, Rat.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.88,1:32:26.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是你们需要的电磁场区域资料\N{\rEng}here's the EM Field data that you're primed for.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.98,1:32:29.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,多谢  “老鼠”\N{\rEng}Digging that, Rat.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.49,1:32:30.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是它\N{\rEng}Primed for.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.65,1:32:31.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是它\N{\rEng}Primed for.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.89,1:32:34.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,关键性数据\N{\rEng}Prime numbers
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.76,1:32:36.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\bord1}{\shad1}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H111111&}{\4c&H111111&}1  2  3  5\None, two, three, five,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.13,1:32:39.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\bord1}{\shad1}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H111111&}{\4c&H111111&}7  11  13  17\Nseven, eleven, thirteen, seventeen...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.60,1:32:47.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}我不喜欢“命运”  我可以帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.70,1:32:58.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}我们需要时间  找到“命运”  延迟它的发射
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.39,1:33:04.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们开始吧\N{\rEng}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.55,1:33:18.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}命运计划  阿拉斯加
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.01,1:33:29.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯\N{\rEng}James.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.35,1:33:37.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,长官\N{\rEng}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.69,1:33:40.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,是  长官\N{\rEng}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.02,1:33:43.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,开始吧  伙计们\N{\rEng}Here we go, folks.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.03,1:33:45.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,这次它终于工作了\N{\rEng}Okay, this time it's going to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.50,1:33:47.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  就这样  继续  继续\N{\rEng}Here you go... beautiful. Yeah, mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.93,1:33:48.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rEng}Come on, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.93,1:33:51.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,继续  我还想再看一次天空\N{\rEng}Come on, Daddy wants to see the sky again.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.84,1:33:56.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,好  好  我们再来一次\N{\rEng}Okay, okay, okay. Let's try again.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.44,1:33:57.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,注意  扭矩是R\N{\rEng}Your torque is R,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.71,1:33:59.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,穿过F点\N{\rEng}cross F...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.24,1:34:01.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的R点太小了  约书亚\N{\rEng}No, your R is too small, Josh.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.58,1:34:02.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rEng}Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.61,1:34:03.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\rEng}Wait, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.61,1:34:04.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在笑什么\N{\rEng}What are you laughing at?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.98,1:34:08.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我还有其他几百个精英\N{\rEng}No, I mean, it took me and 400 of the world's smartest people
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.32,1:34:09.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,设计了A计划\N{\rEng}to come up with the first plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.05,1:34:11.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想帮忙吗\N{\rEng}You want to help?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.22,1:34:13.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  我只想掉头回家\N{\rEng}No. I want to turn around and go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.46,1:34:14.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是不可能的\N{\rEng}It's not going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.99,1:34:16.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么  我们都会死\N{\rEng}Well, then we're going to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.06,1:34:18.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rEng}True.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.00,1:34:19.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想想\N{\rEng}All right, look,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.62,1:34:21.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,-让我们从这个正方形开始 -好的　　　　　　　　　\N{\rEng}-let's start from square one. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.23,1:34:22.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们从这个正方形开始\N{\rEng}Let's start from square one.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.23,1:34:25.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,这部分与密度的关系十分密切\N{\rEng}The bulk modules-- depends on density.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.34,1:34:27.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的扭矩是R  穿过F点\N{\rEng}Your torque is R cross F,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.34,1:34:30.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是你要先对体积求积分\N{\rEng}but you have to integrate volume...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.17,1:34:34.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是  这里  看看  这里\N{\rEng}But here, here... just consider this.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.71,1:34:39.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在  我们\N{\rEng}Now, we got this...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.15,1:34:40.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  穿过F点\N{\rEng}Okay, now, R cross F,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.75,1:34:43.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经把派值考虑进去了\N{\rEng}we're putting in pi. What's V?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.25,1:34:45.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,看在上帝的份上\N{\rEng}Oh, for God's sake!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.02,1:34:47.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好  让我再打他一顿\N{\rEng}All right. I'm hitting him again.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.39,1:34:48.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  不\N{\rEng}No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.43,1:34:50.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,布雷兹  不  你瞧  我有个意见\N{\rEng}Braz, no, look, I have a theory.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.80,1:34:52.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,有兴趣听吗\N{\rEng}Are you interested?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.70,1:34:54.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们都听着\N{\rEng}Yes. We're interested.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.10,1:34:56.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,先让我抽只烟  然后听我说\N{\rEng}Then let me smoke a cigarette, and I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.51,1:35:07.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,感谢上帝\N{\rEng}Oh, thank God.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.68,1:35:10.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好  你瞧\N{\rEng}All right, fine, look.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.58,1:35:13.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要冲击波产生干涉式反应  对吧\N{\rEng}Look, we have to use wave interference, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.12,1:35:14.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,一次爆炸是不能产生这样效果的\N{\rEng}Because one explosion won't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.05,1:35:16.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,试想一下池塘里面得石头\N{\rEng}Think about stones in a pond.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.69,1:35:18.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,把一块大石头扔进池塘\N{\rEng}You drop a large stone into a pond,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.66,1:35:19.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,有很多水滴会飞溅起来\N{\rEng}you get a big splash,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.89,1:35:21.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后就结束了\N{\rEng}and then that's it, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.59,1:35:25.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是如果扔一块小石头进去  等到水波慢慢稀疏\N{\rEng}But drop a smaller stone, wait until the ripples weaken
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.40,1:35:30.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后再扔进去一块小石头\N{\rEng}and drop another and another, and another, and fluid dynamics 101.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.73,1:35:33.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,水波的能量将以几何级数的速度增长\N{\rEng}The ripples reinforce each other in geometric progression.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.37,1:35:35.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,整体大于局部之和\N{\rEng}Hm, the whole bigger than the sum of the parts.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.04,1:35:37.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,这样我们可以将五个\N{\rEng}Then we'll have five
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.21,1:35:39.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,200兆吨级的炸弹\N{\rEng}200 megaton explosions...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.58,1:35:41.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,分别进行引爆\N{\rEng}Instead of one big bang.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.18,1:35:43.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,用电线短路方法起动核仪器\N{\rEng}So, we hot-wire the nukes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.25,1:35:44.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.25,1:35:45.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,代替一次大爆炸\N{\rEng}And as one does,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.25,1:35:47.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们把这些炸弹精确地\N{\rEng}we seed them through the core...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.15,1:35:50.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,放到地核里面\N{\rEng}at locations that have to be accurate to the inch.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.19,1:35:54.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后按照预定的顺序引爆\N{\rEng}We detonate them in a sequence that has to be accurate to the millisecond...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.56,1:35:58.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,这将是历史上规模最大的一次核爆\N{\rEng}then we outrun the biggest nuclear shock wave in history.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.93,1:35:59.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rEng}Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.06,1:36:01.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.93,1:36:05.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想这应该是很简单的\N{\rEng}I mean, that should be fairly simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.98,1:36:14.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,“命运”准备完毕\N{\rEng}Destiny now should be diverting to the central.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.34,1:36:17.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,最后一次校正\N{\rEng}Final calibration
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.08,1:36:19.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,所有发射系统\N{\rEng}on both transmission systems...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.32,1:36:21.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}能源资料部
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.96,1:36:24.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}无法进入
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.45,1:36:26.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\rEng}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.32,1:36:27.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,切断\N{\rEng}Cut the... cut the rouge.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.56,1:36:30.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,电路上方的红色电线\N{\rEng}The red wire above the circuit.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.26,1:36:31.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  好的\N{\rEng}Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.26,1:36:32.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,不对  等等\N{\rEng}No, no, wait, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.33,1:36:34.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  应该是电路下方的红色电线\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, cut it below.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.20,1:36:39.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\rEng}Please...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.01,1:36:45.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,A区  B区\N{\rEng}Extensions A, B.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.71,1:36:46.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,-准备  -能量检查\N{\rEng}-Here we go. -F, check.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.78,1:36:48.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,将反应堆的能量加到15\N{\rEng}Increase power to reactors ten through 15
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.01,1:36:51.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,已经准备好了\N{\rEng}We're almost there, folks.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.25,1:37:16.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}限制
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.10,1:37:38.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}42小时  深度2600英里
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.69,1:37:45.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们  我们已经接近里核了\N{\rEng}Okay, guys we're closing on the inner core.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.94,1:37:48.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,核弹已经准备好了\N{\rEng}The nukes are ready. Timers are on.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.34,1:37:51.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好  准备投弹\N{\rEng}Great. Let's start dropping them.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.60,1:37:53.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是这里的压力太大了  炸弹受不了\N{\rEng}No. The bombs are not built for these pressures.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.74,1:37:55.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以这些炸弹外面都有保护层\N{\rEng}That's why they were in that pod.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.51,1:37:56.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你现在投弹\N{\rEng}If you send them out now...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.85,1:37:58.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们立刻就会爆炸\N{\rEng}out of that casing, they'll be crushed instantly.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.75,1:37:59.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么我们有D计划吗\N{\rEng}I'm assuming we have a Plan D.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.85,1:38:01.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,D计划就是我们用维吉尔本身做核弹的外壳\N{\rEng}Plan D is Virgil's compartments.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.32,1:38:02.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们把核弹\N{\rEng}We put a nuke in
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.32,1:38:03.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,分别放置好\N{\rEng}each section of Virgil
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.49,1:38:05.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后每次去掉一个保护层\N{\rEng}and then eject the individual sections one at a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.56,1:38:07.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,它们应该能够坚持一段时间\N{\rEng}They should stay intact long enough for the nuke to go off.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.72,1:38:11.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.53,1:38:15.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是在一切正常的情况下  维吉尔号不会自动脱落的\N{\rEng}Virgil's not designed to eject undamaged compartments.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.50,1:38:17.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是总有一个控制机构\N{\rEng}Okay, these are the ejection mechanisms
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.83,1:38:19.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,来控制各部分的动作\N{\rEng}holding each compartment in place.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.87,1:38:22.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些部分就被一个“关键点”联接着\N{\rEng}They're all connected by one master hydraulic gear.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.04,1:38:25.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,就好像是钥匙圈一样\N{\rEng}Kind of like keys on a key ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.91,1:38:28.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们要做的 就是用钥匙打开它\N{\rEng}What we have to do, we have to unlock the piston.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.78,1:38:30.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,这样所有的部分就会散开\N{\rEng}That will release the compartments
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.85,1:38:32.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,这样炸弹就可以被引爆了\N{\rEng}so the bombs can be jettisoned.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.45,1:38:33.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么这个“关键点”在哪里\N{\rEng}Where's the master gear?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.82,1:38:36.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,就在引擎喷口附近\N{\rEng}In the crawl space we used to get out earlier.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.69,1:38:37.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,它怎么在那里\N{\rEng}Well, what the hell is it doing there?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.99,1:38:39.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只用了三个月的时间来建造这艘船\N{\rEng}I built the ship in three damn months.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.49,1:38:40.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不是故意怠工\N{\rEng}I didn't think I'd be
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.62,1:38:42.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\rEng}intentionally sabotaging it. I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.36,1:38:43.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么我们有一个人必须去了\N{\rEng}So one of us has to go in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.63,1:38:44.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rEng}Correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.55,1:38:47.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,那里的温度有9000多度\N{\rEng}Into the crawl space that has core fluid at 9, 000 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.52,1:38:48.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.23,1:38:49.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能用液化氮把那里淹没吗\N{\rEng}Can you flush it with liquid nitrogen?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.77,1:38:51.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的液化氮不够了\N{\rEng}We don't have enough at this point.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.07,1:38:52.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,9000度\N{\rEng}9, 000 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.54,1:38:54.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们的工作服只能抵挡\N{\rEng}And our suits are built to withstand...?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.57,1:38:56.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,4500度\N{\rEng}Half that, probably.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.21,1:38:57.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,很错  只有一半\N{\rEng}Right. Half that.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.24,1:38:58.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以你的意思是\N{\rEng}So what you're saying is
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.68,1:39:00.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,无论谁去那里  肯定是回不来了\N{\rEng}whoever goes into that crawl space, is not coming back.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.95,1:39:11.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起\N{\rEng}Together.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.90,1:39:13.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.66,1:39:15.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,稍等\N{\rEng}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.26,1:39:16.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我数三下  -好的　　\N{\rEng}-On three. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.06,1:39:19.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\bord1}{\shad1}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H111111&}{\4c&H111111&}1  2  3\NOne... two... three.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.31,1:39:36.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,看来我最好去准备准备\N{\rEng}Well, I better go on, get myself ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.85,1:39:37.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  布雷兹  等一下\N{\rEng}No, Braz, wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.01,1:39:39.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,布雷兹  等一下\N{\rEng}No, Braz, no wait. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.62,1:39:41.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,等等  我能不能看看\N{\rEng}Just a moment, may I see that?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.28,1:39:42.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,-不行  -让我看看\N{\rEng}-No. -May l?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.32,1:39:43.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,行吗\N{\rEng}May l?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.32,1:39:44.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.09,1:39:46.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.42,1:39:48.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,小戏法\N{\rEng}Magic.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.19,1:39:53.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,布雷兹  这三根线的长度相等\N{\rEng}I mean, Braz, three straws of equal length.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.26,1:39:54.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说  这太孩子气了\N{\rEng}I mean, this is childish.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.96,1:39:55.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们再来一次\N{\rEng}Let's do it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.88,1:39:57.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,用不着了\N{\rEng}No, we will not do it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.21,1:39:59.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想你一定很高兴吧\N{\rEng}I thought you'd be happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.97,1:40:00.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  但是你也\N{\rEng}No. Not at the expense
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.97,1:40:02.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,不应该这样做\N{\rEng}of you making us look like fools.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.44,1:40:04.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,他是对的  你为什么要抢着去做英雄\N{\rEng}He's right. Why do you get dibs on being the hero?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.74,1:40:06.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为这是我的船\N{\rEng}Because it's my damn ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.24,1:40:07.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,这就足够了吗\N{\rEng}Oh, that makes perfect sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.19,1:40:11.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗  20年来  除了维吉尔号我一无所有\N{\rEng}Look, for 20 years, I've done nothing but Virgil. 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.45,1:40:12.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,维吉尔号是我的唯一\N{\rEng}Virgil belongs to me,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.85,1:40:14.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何我不能让它毁坏\N{\rEng}and I will not let her fail.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.62,1:40:15.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不允许\N{\rEng}I will not.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.95,1:40:18.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想知道这艘船对我\N{\rEng}Now if you want to know what's worth dying for
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.22,1:40:19.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,来说多重要\N{\rEng}this ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.22,1:40:22.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,为了保全它\N{\rEng}Building it instead of imagining it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.29,1:40:26.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,我宁愿用我的血去保卫它\N{\rEng}If Virgil needs more blood, it will be my blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.60,1:40:28.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在我要去\N{\rEng}Now I am going to go
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.80,1:40:30.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,准备了\N{\rEng}and get ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.94,1:40:43.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了\N{\rEng}Good to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.05,1:40:49.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,小贝\N{\rEng}Beck.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.62,1:40:51.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,约书亚\N{\rEng}Josh.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.32,1:40:56.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,你造了一艘好船  布雷兹\N{\rEng}It's a hell of a boat you built, Braz.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.99,1:41:01.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,能认识你们我很荣幸\N{\rEng}I am really proud to have known you guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.36,1:41:03.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.99,1:41:25.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,布雷兹\N{\rEng}Braz.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.52,1:41:27.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,爱德华\N{\rEng}Edward.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.72,1:41:31.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了  康拉德\N{\rEng}Yes, Conrad?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.66,1:41:33.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是对的\N{\rEng}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.26,1:41:35.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的船\N{\rEng}It is your ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.10,1:41:38.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在它是我们的\N{\rEng}But I wish to God it had been ours.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.72,1:42:05.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,快要打开密封门了\N{\rEng}The chamber's sealed, Beck.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.23,1:42:07.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,准备\N{\rEng}Ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.34,1:42:11.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,打开舱门\N{\rEng}Open the hatch.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.64,1:42:52.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,挺住  布雷兹\N{\rEng}Hang on, Braz.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.31,1:42:54.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,挺住\N{\rEng}Come on, hang on.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.66,1:43:49.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,手动解体系统启动\N{\rEng}Manual override is complete!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.83,1:43:51.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,布雷兹  我们还能把你弄出来\N{\rEng}Braz, we can still get you out of there.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.81,1:43:58.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,走  你们走吧  打开推进器\N{\rEng}No... start... start the impeller.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.81,1:44:03.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.97,1:44:32.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有事情要做\N{\rEng}We got a job to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.04,1:44:34.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,开始吧\N{\rEng}Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.24,1:44:36.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\rEng}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.61,1:44:40.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,磁防护系统启动完毕\N{\rEng}Magnetic shielding systems are up.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.92,1:44:42.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,能量85%\N{\rEng}Power level's 85%.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.12,1:44:43.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,反应堆能量提高到10\N{\rEng}Increase power to Reactor 10.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.05,1:44:46.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,所有人员撤离\N{\rEng}All personnel should be clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.66,1:44:54.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}禁止进入
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.04,1:45:03.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\rEng}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.64,1:45:04.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,啊  对不起\N{\rEng}Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.74,1:45:10.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了  行了\N{\rEng}Okay, she's down.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.88,1:45:13.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,接近第一投放点\N{\rEng}Approaching the first drop-off point.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.75,1:45:15.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们要加速了  伙计们\N{\rEng}We got to be accurate to the second here, boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.62,1:45:20.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,3-5分钟内投放第二枚\N{\rEng}And drop in three-five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.22,1:45:23.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,计时器启动\N{\rEng}And... timer on.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.39,1:45:24.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,拉出来\N{\rEng}Pull it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.56,1:45:31.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,准备\N{\rEng}Clear... and...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.30,1:45:32.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,投放\N{\rEng}ejecting.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.48,1:45:42.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  准备启动\N{\rEng}All right. Initiate firing sequence.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.51,1:45:43.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,长官\N{\rEng}Sir...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.52,1:45:46.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们最后的任务了  史迪克\N{\rEng}It's our last shot, Stick.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.42,1:45:47.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,去你的\N{\rEng}Damn you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.65,1:45:50.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,去我的  太晚了\N{\rEng}Damn me? Too late.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.15,1:45:53.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\bord1}{\shad1}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H111111&}{\4c&H111111&}10  9  8\NTen, nine, eight...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.06,1:45:57.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\rEng}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.94,1:46:00.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}命运计划中央控制
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.43,1:46:02.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是你\N{\rEng}Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.67,1:46:05.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\bord1}{\shad1}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H111111&}{\4c&H111111&}4  3  2\N...four, three, two...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.04,1:46:08.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,有人把能源全部转移了\N{\rEng}Someone's diverted our energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.64,1:46:10.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些能源都跑哪去了\N{\rEng}Where the hell's it gone?!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.94,1:46:13.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,看起来好像是\N{\rEng}It looks like...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.71,1:46:15.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,兔子岛\N{\rEng}Coney lsland.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.78,1:46:20.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们的功夫还差点\N{\rEng}Your Kung Fu is not strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.57,1:46:22.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,把能源转移回来需要多长时间\N{\rEng}Well, how long will it take to get it back online?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.77,1:46:24.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么  尽快！\N{\rEng}Well, then get to it!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.53,1:46:34.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,将军\N{\rEng}Oh, hey, General.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.63,1:46:37.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,有什么事吗\N{\rEng}Is there something I can do for you?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.84,1:46:43.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,计时器启动\N{\rEng}Timer on.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.05,1:46:45.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,准备\N{\rEng}Clear...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.78,1:46:46.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,分离！\N{\rEng}ejecting.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.32,1:46:55.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,分离\N{\rEng}Ejecting.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.55,1:47:00.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,拉出来\N{\rEng}Pull it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.96,1:47:02.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.29,1:47:04.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,准备把最后一块  200兆吨的石头扔进池塘\N{\rEng}Let's go throw our last little 200 megaton stone in the pond.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.96,1:47:08.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,不知道这些核弹激起的波纹是什么样的\N{\rEng}I always wanted to make a splash in nuclear physics.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.13,1:47:08.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这些能量的传播方式\N{\rEng}You know, that energy propagation stuff
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.93,1:47:10.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是说\N{\rEng}you were talking about...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.13,1:47:10.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  大学物理里面就讲过\N{\rEng}Oh, that was high school physics.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.96,1:47:11.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,对  但是仍然不够准确\N{\rEng}Yeah, it's not exactly...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.79,1:47:13.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只是根据地核的MRI定律计算的\N{\rEng}I just took the wavelengths from the core fluidoff the MRl readings.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.60,1:47:16.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,-对  然后乘以800  -600\N{\rEng}-Yeah, and multiplied by 800... -600
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.03,1:47:21.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,确定但你补充了MRI偏压\N{\rEng}Surely you compensated for the MRl bias.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.88,1:47:23.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,快重新设定定时器\N{\rEng}We got to reset the timers!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.25,1:47:26.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,重新定时  不  没用的\N{\rEng}Reset the timers! No! It just won't work.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.02,1:47:28.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是定时器的问题  它本身就不够\N{\rEng}It's not the timers! This is not enough!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.92,1:47:29.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么不够\N{\rEng}What's not enough?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.92,1:47:31.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,这枚核弹的力量还不足以\N{\rEng}The last bomb is not enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.15,1:47:32.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,完成整个冲击波链\N{\rEng}T o complete the wave form.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.42,1:47:34.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,对  最后一枚炸弹的爆炸力必须增加30%\N{\rEng}Yeah. No. The last bomb has to be 30% larger.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.62,1:47:36.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,大约需要六到七公斤的钚\N{\rEng}That's six or seven pounds of plutonium.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.19,1:47:38.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼  我们哪有这么多的钚\N{\rEng}Where are we going to get six or seven pounds of plutonium?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.10,1:47:47.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,小心  船体受到突发\N{\rEng}Guys, we got hit
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.70,1:47:48.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,力量的冲击\N{\rEng}by an energy flare.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.70,1:47:50.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,分离过程无法中止\N{\rEng}I can't keep us on course.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.14,1:47:51.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,喷射仓将在50秒种后开启\N{\rEng}Ejecting compartment in 50 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.04,1:47:53.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  小贝  等等  用力推\N{\rEng}No, Beck! No, wait! No! Push it!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.61,1:47:55.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,你也推\N{\rEng}You push it!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.71,1:47:57.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们怎么了  我听不到你们了\N{\rEng}Come on, guys, I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.55,1:48:00.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,它压在我的肩膀上了\N{\rEng}It's got my shoulder!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.51,1:48:01.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,推\N{\rEng}Push!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.26,1:48:03.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\rEng}Guys!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.32,1:48:04.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了吗\N{\rEng}Clear!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.42,1:48:06.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,快从喷射仓里面出来  你们在干什么\N{\rEng}Clear the compartment! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.12,1:48:08.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的振动好像把通讯器弄坏了\N{\rEng}I think the flare has knocked the Coms out.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.72,1:48:09.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,不行  推不动  约书亚  推不动\N{\rEng}I can't get it, Josh. I can't get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.26,1:48:10.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\rEng}Go...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.59,1:48:12.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\rEng}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.33,1:48:13.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.36,1:48:15.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  对不起\N{\rEng}I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.07,1:48:18.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,能听到吗\N{\rEng}Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.13,1:48:20.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,喷射仓就要开启了\N{\rEng}I'm correcting course. Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.44,1:48:27.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,辛斯基\N{\rEng}Zimsky!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.91,1:48:30.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.22,1:48:35.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,用力推\N{\rEng}Push it!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.55,1:48:39.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,喷射仓将在10秒种之内开启\N{\rEng}Ejecting compartment in ten seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.79,1:48:41.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,能听到吗\N{\rEng}Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.29,1:48:43.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,约书亚  快走  快走\N{\rEng}Josh, go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.26,1:48:44.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,出去\N{\rEng}Get out! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.99,1:48:48.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,快给我出去  现在\N{\rEng}Now! Get out! Now! Get out! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.31,1:49:02.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,约书亚\N{\rEng}Josh.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.44,1:49:05.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,用反应堆的\N{\rEng}For the last bomb, to make it larger...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.55,1:49:08.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,钚环来提高核弹的威力\N{\rEng}use the fuel rods from the react...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.45,1:49:11.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,分离\N{\rEng}Ejecting.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.09,1:49:19.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,我必须要\N{\rEng}I got to get...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.23,1:49:21.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,必须去\N{\rEng}I got to...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.43,1:49:24.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,小贝\N{\rEng}Beck.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.53,1:49:25.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,小贝  听到了吗\N{\rEng}Beck, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.73,1:49:28.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,小贝  如果你还有什么好主意  趁现在赶快告诉我\N{\rEng}Beck, if you have any better ideas, you tell me now.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.57,1:49:31.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们只有三分钟来调整下一枚核弹\N{\rEng}We've only got three minutes to eject this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.17,1:49:33.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,小贝\N{\rEng}Beck!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.64,1:49:36.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,我听不到你们\N{\rEng}Come on, guys. I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.88,1:49:41.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,小贝\N{\rEng}Beck.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.46,1:49:53.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}辐射程度
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.51,1:49:55.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}温度
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.97,1:49:57.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}警告
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.96,1:51:28.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,约书亚  过来\N{\rEng}Josh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.03,1:51:32.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\rEng}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.60,1:51:35.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样\N{\rEng}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.83,1:51:37.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,能帮我摘掉手套吗\N{\rEng}Will you take my gloves off?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.50,1:51:38.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的天哪\N{\rEng}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:38.87,1:51:42.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,帮帮忙\N{\rEng}Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.27,1:51:44.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,我必须这么做\N{\rEng}I had to build the blast.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.51,1:51:45.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\rEng}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.67,1:51:47.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住  我去拿点\N{\rEng}Hold on, let me get...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.38,1:51:50.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  留在这\N{\rEng}No. Stay here for one second.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.11,1:51:52.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才想告诉你\N{\rEng}I was trying to call you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.58,1:51:55.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道通讯器坏了\N{\rEng}I know the Coms were down.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:55.15,1:51:56.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.15,1:51:57.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你做了什么\N{\rEng}I know what you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.75,1:52:00.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经没有足够的能量\N{\rEng}We don't have enough energy...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.16,1:52:01.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rEng}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.16,1:52:02.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,回去了\N{\rEng}...to get back.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.59,1:52:04.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,你做得很好\N{\rEng}You did good.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:04.09,1:52:08.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果是我  我也会这么做\N{\rEng}I would've done the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.23,1:52:09.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,辛斯基呢\N{\rEng}Where's Zimsky?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.17,1:52:14.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,过来\N{\rEng}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.10,1:52:16.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,你做得很好\N{\rEng}You did good.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.04,1:52:19.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,做的好\N{\rEng}You did good.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.46,1:52:36.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,一分钟后爆炸\N{\rEng}One minute to the first detonation.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.39,1:52:38.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,12分钟后冲击波将击中我们\N{\rEng}And 12 until the blast hits us.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.20,1:52:46.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,希望我们能窒息而死\N{\rEng}I was hoping we'd suffocate to death first.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.40,1:53:02.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}温度危急
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.77,1:53:22.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,小贝\N{\rEng}Beck.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.77,1:53:25.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,小贝  小贝\N{\rEng}Beck, Beck.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.44,1:53:26.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我能让\N{\rEng}What could you do
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.61,1:53:29.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,推进器转起来  你能把我们弄出去吗\N{\rEng}if I got you enough power to fire the impeller?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.25,1:53:31.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,激光钻头可能不行  但是我可以启动推进器\N{\rEng}Maybe not the laser but the impeller.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.48,1:53:32.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么  能量从哪来呢\N{\rEng}What? From where?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.92,1:53:34.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,地核的热量\N{\rEng}The heat of the core.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.85,1:53:36.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,足足9000度的高温\N{\rEng}It's 9, 000 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.65,1:53:38.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以把热量转为我们需要的能源\N{\rEng}Unobtainium converts heat to energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.82,1:53:42.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,这艘船就象是一块太阳能电池\N{\rEng}So this whole damn ship is like a big, old solar panel.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.16,1:53:43.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,来  我需要你的帮助\N{\rEng}Come on, I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.33,1:53:52.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,已经有两枚核弹爆炸了\N{\rEng}Number two's going!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.22,1:54:16.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,只有在无限的未知中\N{\rEng}For here in the great infinite unknowable...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.83,1:54:21.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,人们才能知道最重要的事情是什么\N{\rEng}man can come to know the most important thing of all
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.40,1:54:24.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,他自己\N{\rEng}himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.47,1:54:26.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,他能知道\N{\rEng}He can understand...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.10,1:54:30.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,我他妈的到底在做什么\N{\rEng}What the fuck am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.74,1:55:09.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,起作用了\N{\rEng}We've got full rotation!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.98,1:55:11.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,正常运转了\N{\rEng}It's turning!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.82,1:55:22.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\rEng}All right!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:29.93,1:55:31.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,快点  小贝  在哪里\N{\rEng}Come on, Beck, where is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.40,1:55:35.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\rEng}Come on. Come on, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.31,1:55:36.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是最后一个吗\N{\rEng}Is that the last one?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:36.87,1:55:39.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.28,1:55:49.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,再等几秒钟\N{\rEng}Give it a couple seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.91,1:56:00.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,启动了\N{\rEng}It worked!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.57,1:56:15.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,准备感受力量吧\N{\rEng}Get ready to pull a few G's.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.50,1:56:35.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,船速420节\N{\rEng}420 knots.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.62,1:56:37.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,这才像布雷兹的船\N{\rEng}Now, this is more like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.00,1:56:38.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,440节\N{\rEng}440.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.87,1:56:48.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事  这里也会有地震\N{\rEng}So, Rat, what's the center of this quake?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.34,1:56:48.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,到处都是\N{\rEng}It's everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.51,1:56:51.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是巨大冲击波的结果\N{\rEng}It's one giant shock wave!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.50,1:56:53.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,这颗星球在给它自己加热\N{\rEng}The planet's healing itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.50,1:56:57.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们就要到家了 第三次回家\N{\rEng}At this speed, we're going to be home in a third of the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.18,1:57:30.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,只要我们能够冲过\N{\rEng}As long as we can surf
Dialogue: 0,1:57:30.25,1:57:31.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些岩浆  我们就安全了\N{\rEng}these magma flows, we'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.75,1:57:34.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,上帝保佑  千万不要冲进死路\N{\rEng}Let's just pray we don't run into any dead ends,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.22,1:57:36.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,或者丢失导航信号\N{\rEng}or we're going to miss those lasers.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:39.70,1:57:43.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,走那边\N{\rEng}Okay, navigator, which way?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:43.48,1:57:45.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想左边是最好的\N{\rEng}We've got greater fluid density on the left.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:45.17,1:57:48.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,跟着岩浆的流向走好了\N{\rEng}Go with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:07.50,1:58:08.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}16小时后
Dialogue: 0,1:58:08.76,1:58:10.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,比尔  他们在向哪里开\N{\rEng}Bill, where are they headed?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:10.09,1:58:12.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们好像在夏威夷\N{\rEng}Looks like she found a space between
Dialogue: 0,1:58:12.26,1:58:14.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,附近找到了一条出路\N{\rEng}some tectonic plates somewhere near Hawaii.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.35,1:58:21.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,约书亚\N{\rEng}Josh...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:21.97,1:58:22.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经接近地表了\N{\rEng}They're closing in on us too fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:22.81,1:58:24.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道我能不能\N{\rEng}I don't know if I can...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.54,1:58:25.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\rEng}Hey, you got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:37.36,1:58:38.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}讯号中断
Dialogue: 0,1:58:40.86,1:58:46.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,找不到他们了  史迪克  我\N{\rEng}Um... w-we lost them, Stick, and I...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.59,1:59:00.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}四小时后
Dialogue: 0,1:59:07.32,1:59:09.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的能源呢\N{\rEng}Where'd our power go?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:10.78,1:59:12.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的能源来自地核的热量\N{\rEng}Well, we're powered by the heat.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:12.46,1:59:14.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里太冷了\N{\rEng}It's stone cold down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:19.33,1:59:22.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,想想好的一面\N{\rEng}Look on the bright side.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:23.54,1:59:26.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,起码我们不会活活被热死\N{\rEng}At least we're not going to boil to death.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:26.00,1:59:27.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,你总是能看到积极的一面吗\N{\rEng}You always look on the bright side?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.76,1:59:29.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rEng}Always.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:30.34,1:59:33.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  再想想\N{\rEng}Okay, let's assess
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.68,1:59:37.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,通讯装备已经不能用了\N{\rEng}We've got no communications,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.35,1:59:39.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们应该在海面下800英尺\N{\rEng}we're probably 800 feet down,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:39.85,1:59:42.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,但也可能是800英里\N{\rEng}but we might as well be 800 miles.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:42.27,1:59:44.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们对外界的情况一无所知\N{\rEng}We're in an Unobtainium
Dialogue: 0,1:59:44.93,1:59:47.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,声呐系统也不能直接找到我们\N{\rEng}cigar tube with the sonar signature of a rock.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:47.92,1:59:50.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们得想点办法让声纳能听到我们\N{\rEng}We've got just enough power to make the ultrasonics burp,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.23,1:59:51.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是好像已经\N{\rEng}but no one's listening
Dialogue: 0,1:59:51.59,1:59:53.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有人用这些频率了\N{\rEng}on those frequencies anyway, and...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.03,1:59:56.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,甚至没人知道我们还活着\N{\rEng}nobody even knows we're alive.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:02.04,2:00:04.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:04.37,2:00:06.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,给我一分钟\N{\rEng}Give me a minute on this one.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:13.33,2:00:16.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}夏威夷海岸
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.73,2:00:25.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,完全没希望\N{\rEng}This is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:25.61,2:00:27.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,将军  我们已经离得这么近了\N{\rEng}Come on, General, we've got to be getting close.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:27.77,2:00:27.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能\N{\rEng}We can't...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.00,2:00:30.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,“老鼠”先生  就算他们还活着\N{\rEng}Mr. Rat, even if they were still alive,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:30.10,2:00:32.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们也没办法和我们取得联系\N{\rEng}there's no way they could contact us.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:33.30,2:00:35.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里是舰桥\N{\rEng}Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:35.25,2:00:38.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,船长  我们的潜艇扫描到一些东西\N{\rEng}Skipper, Combat relays that our sub has something on the sonar.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:38.41,2:00:39.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,在哪里\N{\rEng}Where do they think?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:39.12,2:00:41.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,比尔  再听一下\N{\rEng}Bill, put it up on the hydrophone.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:46.27,2:00:47.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,鲸鱼  先生\N{\rEng}Whales, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:47.07,2:00:48.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些鲸鱼本来不应该在这里出现\N{\rEng}They're a long way off their usual path,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:48.32,2:00:50.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过这也不是什么不可思议的事情\N{\rEng}but that's not uncommon since that, uh...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:50.12,2:00:51.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,这应该怎么称呼\N{\rEng}what are they calling it?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:51.39,2:00:52.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,轨道漂移\N{\rEng}Orbital wobble?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:52.39,2:00:54.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  他们就是这么称呼\N{\rEng}Yeah, that's what they call it.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:54.12,2:00:56.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么  谢谢你  船长\N{\rEng}Well, thank you very much, Captain,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:56.63,2:00:59.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们的任务已经结束了\N{\rEng}but I think we're done here.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:59.11,2:01:01.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,将军\N{\rEng}General.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:03.23,2:01:05.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,J.O.  我是船长\N{\rEng}J.O., this is the captain.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:05.07,2:01:07.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,行动中止\N{\rEng}Stand down from SAR Operations.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:39.93,2:01:42.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,是鲸  是鲸\N{\rEng}It's whales! It's whales!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:42.73,2:01:45.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,将军\N{\rEng}Hey! General!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:45.66,2:01:46.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,史迪克\N{\rEng}Stick!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:46.78,2:01:47.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是鲸\N{\rEng}It's whales!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:47.99,2:01:48.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,鲸也能发出超声波\N{\rEng}The ultrasonics!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:48.98,2:01:50.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,它们正在为维吉尔号发信号\N{\rEng}They're singing to them!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:50.75,2:01:52.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,你要找到那些鲸鱼\N{\rEng}You gotta find the whales!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:11.00,2:02:14.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,Alpha X  这是NE610\N{\rEng}Alpha X Ray, this is November Echo six one zero.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:14.54,2:02:15.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,我换一下位置\N{\rEng}I'm changing...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:15.83,2:02:18.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,等等  我已经看到那些鲸鱼了\N{\rEng}Hold on, I'm seeing those whales now.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:18.77,2:02:21.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是一场精彩的水戏\N{\rEng}Okay, ball's in the water.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.42,2:02:23.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些鲸鱼在围着什么东西不停的旋转\N{\rEng}This is neat. Those whales are circling something.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:23.18,2:02:24.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,稍等  听\N{\rEng}Hold on, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.38,2:02:25.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,有一组特别强烈的回声\N{\rEng}We have a strong echo here.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:25.78,2:02:26.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,深度800英尺\N{\rEng}Depth, 800 feet.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:26.78,2:02:28.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,那里一定有东西\N{\rEng}There-there's something down there.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.48,2:02:30.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,一定有东西沉在那里了\N{\rEng}There's definitely something down there.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:13.36,2:03:15.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你  这些超声波一定有用\N{\rEng}I told you pulsing the ultrasonics would work.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:16.03,2:03:19.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,你从来没有感到过累吗\N{\rEng}Do you ever get tired of being right?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:19.37,2:03:20.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:22.37,2:03:24.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,接下来你要做什么\N{\rEng}So what's next for you?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:24.71,2:03:26.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,舒舒服服洗个澡\N{\rEng}A shower.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:28.38,2:03:31.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后我想回NASA\N{\rEng}Then back to NASA, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:31.71,2:03:32.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,你呢\N{\rEng}You?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:32.92,2:03:36.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,猛吃一顿意大利香肠皮萨  加上胡椒粉和圆葱\N{\rEng}Deep-dish pepperoni pizza, green peppers, onions,
Dialogue: 0,2:03:36.59,2:03:42.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,当然还要有蘑菇  然后好好洗个澡  回我的学校去\N{\rEng}extra mushrooms-- then a shower and then back to the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:42.39,2:03:48.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,NASA总算是找到一些好人\N{\rEng}NASA could use a few good men, you know.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:48.20,2:03:49.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:49.53,2:03:52.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过  我的新学生可惨了\N{\rEng}Unfortunately, so could my freshmen geophysics students.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:57.47,2:04:02.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道什么事情让我气愤\N{\rEng}You know what makes me really, really angry?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:02.25,2:04:05.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,鲍勃  赛吉  布雷兹  辛斯基\N{\rEng}Bob, Serge, Braz, Zimsky...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:05.35,2:04:08.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有人会知道他们做了什么  他们为什么去死\N{\rEng}no one's going to ever know what they did or why they died.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:11.02,2:04:13.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,除非\N{\rEng}Unless...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:14.02,2:04:16.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,莫名其妙的这些事情就泄露了\N{\rEng}it all got out somehow.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:18.89,2:04:21.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是莫名其妙\N{\rEng}That's unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:21.70,2:04:22.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rEng}Yeah.
