Dialogue: 0,2:05:35.97,2:05:38.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,…是太空总署的船长  宇航员鲍勃·艾弗森博士\N{\rEng}was captained by NASA astronaut Dr. Bob lverson.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:38.47,2:05:40.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,爱德华·布雷兹是一个如此\N{\rEng}Edward Brazzleton is a name so...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:40.08,2:05:42.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,康拉德·辛斯基博士的  英勇值得我们每个人永远怀念\N{\rEng}Dr. Conrad Zimsky will be best remembered...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:42.41,2:05:43.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,今天的议会上\N{\rEng}On Capitol Hill today,
Dialogue: 0,2:05:43.55,2:05:45.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都在问同样的问题\N{\rEng}everyone's asking the same question
Dialogue: 0,2:05:45.38,2:05:47.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,“命运”计划到底是什么\N{\rEng}What is Project Destiny?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:50.05,2:05:53.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,“命运”来临了\N{\rEng}Destiny, meet world.
